\id REV - Zyphe
\h APALYNAH
\toc1 APALYNAH JOHAN TEI A HMUHPAW APALYNAH BIA
\toc2 APALYNAH
\toc3 Apaly
\mt1 APALYNAH
\mt2 JOHAN TEI A HMUHPAW APALYNAH BIA
\c 1
\s1 Biahmehrui
\p 
\v 1 Ma heh Zisu Khri apalynah cang ka, a va chuh lepaw khah a sae sahlo hmuh sá pawtah Khazing tah a pehpaw a cang. Ama taco a sae Johan khatah a vaiming khah taw ka, a phychua.
\v 2 Johan taco a hmuhpaw vytei cawh thuisah he ka, a thui sahpaw he cawh Khazing bia le Zisu Khri tei a phychuapaw bia cawh a cang.
\v 3 Ma apalynah bia sahlo a reichuapaw maikaw he cawh bonghnang aa ting a. Ma bia sahlo heh thui katei, a bia ciapaw naning tei hratah a cingkaipaw cawh bonghnang aa ting a, zemaw tatah cai cawh a ne myca.
\s1 Kih tlenah le reithainah bia
\p 
\v 4 Johan tah Asia raang chung letei a ungpaw khrisawbu sangsarih sahlo letah ma hrahei a tah he. A ung ciapaw le a ung leimeipaw le a ung lepaw Ama taitah le Abui dyching hme letei a ungpaw thlawpaw sangsarih taitah le,
\v 5 biahnihtu zingchuipaw, thih kaw khawh ly pawtah a tho kaw taw caipaw, aluicung siangpahrang vytei sahlo cung letei naw a hnuipaw Zisu Khri taitah ningdonah le thlawlungnah cawh naa cung letah ung ky seh.
\p A ma dopaw le kaa suanah taitah a thisai tah khaitlawngnah a ma peitu,
\v 6 a Khazing le a Paw a rai hre rua pawtah a tlangbui sahlo le a painah raang cang ruapaw tei a ma tuatu, Ama khatah rungnawnah, hmingtuakhynah vytei cawh chaizaw tah chaizaw tai ung paria thlang ky seh! Amen.
\q1 
\v 7 Ngetua, Ama cawh meding cung lekhei a vong leimei,
\q2 meh vytei tah aa hmuh tae a,
\q1 a kang letei a dongpaw zong takhei aa hmuh a,
\q2 Ama rawng tah aluicung pungpaluh letei ming vytei tah mangchia hratah aa sá a.
\q1 Ma hraco cang ky seh! Amen.
\p 
\v 8 “Kama cawh Alfa le Omeka, a ung ciapaw le a ung leimeipaw le a ung lepaw, Zezong Tuatu ka cang,” tatah Abuipaw Khazing tah a tah.
\s1 Cawngsaw sawcapaw a lopaw
\p 
\v 9 Kama, Johan cawh naa uny ka cang. Taithuinah le a painah raang le mua ingnah letah Zisu khatah kaa zongmingtei tah kaa hrong he peh. Khazing bia le Zisu kong ka reinah rawng tah Patmos tuiraw lang kuapaw ka cang.
\v 10 Abuipaw Ning leco Thlawpaw tah ung neh ka, ka hninglang letah hmoka hratah a thangpaw o cawh ka thui,
\v 11 “Na hmuhpaw vytei cawh cabu letah cia la, Asia raang letei khrisawbu sangsarih sahlo; Efesa khua, Smarna khua, Pergamam khua, Thiatira khua, Sardi khua, Filadelfia khua le Laodisia khua letei a ungpaw sahlo he cawh kua my lo,” tatah a pa tah.
\p 
\v 12 Mataico, bia a pa chingpaw o cawh hmuh du tah ka hninglang ka hui. Ma hratei ka huining taco, sui me-ing chianah tung sangsarih cawh ka hmuh.
\v 13 Ma sui me-ing chianah tung hrong leco, Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a lopaw, a phedong tai paithladih a buhpaw, a cacanghnaw cawh sui tesong tah a rehpaw cawh ka hmuh.\x + \xo 1:13 \xt Dan 7:13\x*
\v 14 Taico, a lu le a sang cawh tuu hming hratah raang ka, huihaw hratah a cang. A meh cawh melui hratah a cang.
\v 15 A phe cawh dakhaipaw, kangpathi ronahpaw me letei ro pathai ciapaw hratah a cang. A o pyraw cawh tuilai pui a calawhpaw py hratah a cang.
\v 16 Taico a kih cacang lang khei esi sangsarih a tle ka, a kaw taico zyzi venang a king le haa tei a tepaw cawh pia ka, a hme cawh ningching a paling licining teipaw hratah a cang.
\p 
\v 17 Ama cawh ka hmuh cangkawleh a phehrang letaco mehthi hratah ka pohly. Taico a kih cacang lang cawh ka cung letah pahnia ka, “Zehmai ci kheh, kama cawh Ahmasaw caipaw le Ahning caipaw,
\v 18 Mehring cawh ka cang, thi neh ka, canghrasala naw thlia tua, chaizaw cawtah ka hring kaw thah! Thihnah le Mehthi khua ingkaw cabi cawh ka hnui,” tatah a pa tah.
\p 
\v 19 “Macawtaco, na hmuh ciapaw le a ung leimeipaw le a hning tah a ung lepaw sahlo khah cia my lo.
\v 20 Ka kih cacang lang letei esi sangsarih na hmuhpaw le sui me-ing chianah tung sangsarih na hmuh pawhe aa biaparuh cawh ma heh a cang. Esi sangsarih cawh khrisawbu sangsarih letei vaiming pasarih cawh a cang he. Sui me-ing chianah tung sangsarih cawh khrisawbu sangsarih khah a cang he,” tatah a tah.
\c 2
\s1 Efesa khua khrisawbu letei cakuapaw
\p 
\v 1 “Efesa khua letei a ungpaw khrisawbu vaiming hai letaco, ma hrahei cia my lo. A kih cacang lang tah esi sangsarih a tlepaw, sui me-ing chianah tung sangsarih hrong letei a khiakaly leimeipaw takhei ma hrahei bia a rei.
\v 2 Na hming tuapaw vytei ka hni, na hre rei a thui zia le mua na ingpaw zong ka hni. Mehchaw ly sahlo khah chethai bei ceh. Apostol cang tlung ly tei ka cang a tahpaw sahlo zong khah pase he ceh ka, a pakheipaw aa cangpaw na hni.
\v 3 Mua ing khynah hnui ceh ka, ka ming rawng tah hanah na ing, canghrasala na ing khy thly thlang.
\v 4 Ma duitei cawh suinah ka ca hnui, zecawtamaw tatah na hnui tawpaw donah khah na bangsai.
\v 5 Na posai ciapaw khah a thui thlang la, a ngepachih la, athoning tei na tuapaw hrakhei tua kaw my lo. Na ngepachih lypaw tei a cang caco, nama khatah a vong neh ka, na me-ing tung khah na chianahpaw taikhei ka palong a.
\v 6 Canghrasala, ma heh na chahnah sangkheh cawh a cang, Nikola a zuipaw sahlo aa hming tuapaw khah a hua ceh ka, ma cawh kama zong tah ka huapaw a cang hrah.
\v 7 Thlawpaw tei khrisawbu sahlo hai letei bia a reipaw heh thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco thui he seh. A tetupaw maikaw cawh Khazing Paradis letei hringnah thingkung taiteipaw cawh ka e sá he a,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Smarna khua khrisawbu letei cakuapaw
\p 
\v 8 “Mataico, Smarna khua letei khrisawbu vaiming hai letaco, ma hrahei cia my lo. Ahmasaw caipaw le Ahning caipaw, thi katei a hringkawpaw takhei ma hrahei bia a rei.
\v 9 Na tai-ing zia le na dawng a chia zia cawh ka hni, canghrasala na dawng a chah. Juda cawngsaw hmuisui a cang tlung lypaw, Setan caw tei synagog letah a pungpaw he Juda cawngsaw ka cang he peh a tahpaw sahlo tei aa ca reipachia zia khah ka hni.
\v 10 Na ing lepaw sahlo cawh ci kheh. Nawthlia tua, Setan taco naa hrong letei thaikhehpaw cawh naaning pase rua pawtah thong letah a ca thla he a, ninghraw chung hanah naa ing a. Thihnah tai zingchui pawtah ung la, hringnah bui lukhu ka ca pae he a.
\v 11 Thlawpaw tei khrisawbu sahlo hai letei bia a reipaw heh thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco thui he seh. A tetupaw maikaw cawh uihning thihnah taco zekhatahmai tah khy a bei he,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Pergamam khua khrisawbu letei cakuapaw
\p 
\v 12 “Pergamam khua letei khrisawbu vaiming hai letaco ma hrahei cia my lo. Zyzi venang a king le haa tei a tepaw a hnuitu takhei ma hrahei bia a rei.
\v 13 Na ungnah letah Setan a bui dyching a ungpaw kong khah ka hni. Canghrasala, ka ming khah a thui thlang ceh ka, ka bia a hnihtu le ka caw tei zingchuipaw Antipa khah, Setan a ungnah naa khuapui letei aa thawning takhei hmai tah na pa zingnah khah thlaw ly teitah na ung.
\v 14 Canghrasala, Balam cawngpahnah a zuipaw sahlo na ungkhuinah rawng he takhei a cawngpe suinah ka ca hnui. Ma cawngsaw taco, nono aa dangpaw batui e sá pawtah le canu capaw suanah lang a nae sá pawtah Israel mingphing sahlo tuhso rua pawtah Balak khah a cawngpah.
\v 15 Ma hraco nama zong tah Nikola a zuipaw sahlo cawngpahnah a zuipaw thaikhehpaw khah na ungkhui hrah he.
\v 16 Macawtaco, a ngepachih tua, na ngepachih ly caco nama khatah a vong tlamang neh ka, ka kaw taitah a kapiapaw zyzi tah aaning cawh ka dy he a.
\v 17 Thlawpaw tei khrisawbu sahlo hai letei bia a reipaw heh, thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco thui he seh. A tetupaw maikaw cawh no thlangpaw manna cawh pei he neh ka, lungrang cung letei ming thapaw a ciapaw zong khah ka peh pai he a. Ma ming cawh aa tingpaw sahlo tah cy ly co ahotahmai hnih a bei he,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Thiatira khua khrisawbu letei cakuapaw
\p 
\v 18 “Taico, Thiatira khua letei khrisawbu vaiming hai letaco ma hrahei cia my lo. Khazing Sawcapaw, melui hratei a cangpaw meh a hnuipaw, a phe cawh daa akhaipaw hratei a cangpaw takhei ma hrahei bia a rei.
\v 19 Na hming tuapaw vytei khah ka hni thlu. Ma cawh donah na hnuipaw, zingnah na hnuipaw, rai na hre pahpaw he le mua na ingpaw le athoning tei navy tah atoheh rai na hre vypaw zong ka hni thlu.
\v 20 Canghrasala, suisenah ka ca hnui, zecawtamaw tatah khuavang pakhei a cangpaw Jezebel aa tahpaw canuno khah na ungkhui. Ma cawngsawno tei, ahmang lypaw a cawngpah pawhe takhei ka sae sahlo khah a pheilanah le nono dangnah batui enah lang a seikhui he.
\v 21 Taico, ma cawngsawno cawh a pheilanah khah a ngepachih a pawtah cai pei neh ka, canghrasala chi du hlui be.
\v 22 Macawtaco, ama cawh tai-ingnah lakhing letah ka vathlang a, ama khatah a pheipaw maikaw zong angepachihnah aa hnui ly caco, reithui tai-ingnah a sah pui tah aa ing a.
\v 23 A hning a zuipaw sahlo cawh ka thaw thlu he a. Kama cawh lungthing le chunglang a mingtu ka cang tahpaw khah khrisawbu sahlo tah aa hni a. Taico, naa tuasenah cacy hratah ka ca pae he a.
\v 24 Canghrasala, ma canuno cawngpahnah a pawng lypaw le Setan biathuh aa tahpaw a hnih lypaw naaning Thiatira khua cawngsaw mehthaikheh naa cung leco phorih ahringpaw chia a bei neh.
\v 25 Maduitei cawh ka vong kaw hlai vytei naa hnui ciapaw khah a tlethlang my lo.
\v 26 Taico, a tetupaw maikaw le a changnah tai ka rei a ngepaw maikaw he cawh ka Paw taitei ka hmuhpaw hratah mingphing sahlo cung letah nawhnuinah ka pae he a.
\q1 
\v 27 ‘Ama taco thaw cungcahrei tah biace he ka,
\q2 alui bei hratah a khuichy he a.’\x + \xo 2:27 \xt Hlaw 2:9\x*
\m 
\v 28 Taico, duivaw esi cawh ka pae he a.
\v 29 Thlawpaw tei khrisawbu sahlo hai letei bia a reipaw heh thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco thui he seh,” tatah a tah.
\c 3
\s1 Sardi khua khrisawbu letei cakuapaw
\p 
\v 1 “Sardi khua letei khrisawbu vaiming hai letaco, ma hrahei cia my lo. Khazing thlawpaw sangsarih le esi sangsarih a hnuipaw takhei ma hrahei bia a rei. Na hming tuapaw vytei ka hni, a thi ciapaw na cang naná tah ahringpaw na lo.
\v 2 A hrah la, na hnui ciapaw hming, a thi daimangpaw khah a thaw patlung kaw tua. Na hming tuapaw vytei heh ka Khazing meh letah a tlingpaw ung be.
\v 3 Macawtaco naa hmuh ciapaw le naa thui ciapaw khah a cingkai la, ma khah zui la a ngepachih my lo. Na hraw ly caco mehru hratah a vong neh ka, ze cai letah maw ka vong a tahpaw khah hnih bei ceh.
\v 4 Canghrasala Sardi khua lekhei a buhpaw he pai a papia a palui lypaw cawngsaw a cawngtei a ung he. Aaning sahlo cawh pai rangpaw a buá tah kama khatah a cinglai hra he. Zemaw tah pawco aaning cawh ma hratei a tua tlangpaw a cang he.
\v 5 A tetupaw maikaw cawh ma hraco pai rangpaw a buh sá tah ung he ka, mataico hringnah cabu chung taico aa ming cawh thehly bei neh. Ka Paw hme le a vaiming sahlo hme leco aa ming cawh ka cang khui hri he a.
\v 6 Thlawpaw tei khrisawbu sahlo hai letei bia a reipaw heh thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco thui he seh,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Filadelfia khua khrisawbu letei cakuapaw
\p 
\v 7 “Filadelfia khua letei khrisawbu vaiming hai letaco ma hrahei cia my lo. Siangpahrang David cabi a hnuipaw, mehpathai le mehding a cangpaw takhei ma hrahei bia a rei. Ama tei a hongpaw ingkaw cawh ahotahmai kha khy be ca ka, Ama tei a khapaw ingkaw cawh ahotahmai hong khy be.
\v 8 Na hming tuapaw vytei ka hni. Thawtlungnah a cawngtei hnui ceh ka, ma hmo co ka bia khah a cingkai ceh ka, ka ming zong a paphah sai be ca ceh ka, ahotahmai kha khy lypaw ingkaw na hme letah ka hong.
\v 9 Nawthlia tua, Setan caw tei synagog letei a pungpaw he, Juda cawngsaw hmuisang cangnah hnui tlung ly tei hingbia rei tei Juda cawngsaw ka cang peh a tahpaw sahlo he cawh taw he neh ka, na hme letah aa khuh ka panaisah he a. Ka ca do hmuisui tahpaw khah ka hnisah he a.
\v 10 Lungsy teitah mua ing pawtah naw ka ca pehpaw na tlethlangnah cawtah alui letei a ungpaw mehnung vytei pase rua pawtei ma khazaw letei a va tlung lepaw pasenah chung taico ka ca bingsá a.
\v 11 Ka vong pating a. Ahotahmai na suilukhu khah aa ca lah pah ly nápawtah na hnui ciapaw khah achaw teitah a tle thlang my lo.
\v 12 A tetupaw maikaw cawh ka Khazing behnah ing leco asuh tung tah ka tua he a. Ma taiteipaw cawh piathlah khaw bei he. Ka Khazingpaw ming, ka Khazingpaw khuapui ming, Jerusalem thapaw, ka Khazingpaw taitah vaicung taitei a za cung lepaw le ka ming thapaw khatah aa cung letah ka cia a.
\v 13 Thlawpaw tei khrisawbu sahlo hai letei bia a reipaw heh thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco thui he seh,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Laodisia khua khrisawbu letei cakuapaw
\p 
\v 14 “Laodisia khua letei khrisawbu vaiming hai letaco ma hrahei cia my lo. Amen a cangpaw bia hnihtu hmuisui le zingchuipaw le mehding a cangpaw, Khazing hming tuapaw a hrangthonah taco, ma hrahei bia a rei.
\v 15 Na hming tuapaw vytei ka hni, cakaw tlung ly, lung tlung ly tei na cangpaw heh. Na lung caco lung lalo la, na cakaw caco cakaw lalo tahpaw ka du.
\v 16 Ma hratei lung tlung ly, cakaw tlung ly, lungpipu tah na cangnah cawtah ka kaw taitah ka ca chothlang a.
\v 17 Ka dawng a chah, ka hnuirung, zehmai a phahlah bei neh na tah, a cang naná tah nama cawh mehsisah, ningdo chuipaw, mehdongchia, mehco, thlekalong tah na cangpaw khah na hnilynah cawtah a cang.
\v 18 Na dawng a chah khy nápawtah me tei ro pase ciapaw sui le na thlekalong muaphynah cawh a lang ly nápawtah pai rang le, na meh khua a hmuh khy nápawtah na meh letei na hne ruapaw mehsi zong kama taitah co la, tahpaw rawhnah ka ca peh.
\v 19 Ka dopaw maikaw cawh cawngpah he neh ka, ka chingrei tei he. Macawtaco chahnai nge la, a ngepachih my lo.
\v 20 Naw thlia tua, ingkaw thahrang letah a daw neh ka, ingkaw ka khong hi. Ahotahmai ka o thui ka, ingkaw a pa hongpaw maikaw cawh ama kha a nae neh ka, batui kaa e hrui a.
\v 21 A tetupaw maikaw cawh kama zong tah te neh katei, ka Paw khatah abui dyching letah ka typaw hratah ka buidyching letah kama khatah a ty hra he a.
\v 22 Thlawpaw tei khrisawbu sahlo hai letei bia a reipaw heh thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco thui he seh,” tatah a tah.
\c 4
\s1 Vaicung letei abui dyching
\p 
\v 1 Ma khy taico a ka huichy neh ka, vaicung letei ingkaw a hongpaw cawh ka hmuh. Taico, o ka thui taw caipaw hmoka hratei a cangpaw taco bia pa ching ka, “Ma lang heh ka kechy tua, ato tai hei hming a ung lepaw sahlo cawh ka ca hmuh sá a,” a pa tah.
\v 2 Sung sungkheh tah Thlawpaw tah va ung neh ka, taico vaicung letaco abui dyching sangkheh cawh hmuh neh ka, ma buidyching cung letaco pakheh a va ty.
\v 3 A va typaw cawh alung ahringpaw jaspar le asaipaw carnilian hmuisang lo ka, taico abui dyching cawh emerald alung hmuisang ky a lopaw mesakupaw tah a cadung.
\v 4 Taico, abui dyching kaekang letaco ahringpaw abui dyching sangki sangpali ung ka, a cung letaco macang paki le papali a ty he. Aa zongmingtei tah pai rangpaw a buh he ka, suilukhu a khu he.
\v 5 Mataico, abui dyching taico lailaw le o le khalung py sahlo cawh va ring caimang ka, abui dyching hme letaco me-ing sangsarih cawh ae ka, ma sahlo cawh Khazing thlawpaw sangsarih khah a cang he.
\v 6 Taico, abui dyching hme leco thlalang hratah a cangpaw rili, kristal alung hratei a pasingpaw cawh ung ka, abui dyching letah le abui dyching kaekang letaco hminghring sangpali, aa hning le hme tei mehkho tei a chih thlangpaw cawh a ung he.
\v 7 Hminghring sangkhehnah cawh cakebarung hratah cang ka, a sanghningnah cawh co tungnypaw hratah a cang, a sangthungnah cawh cawngsaw hme hapaw hme pho ka, a sangpalinah cawh pahmupui a zy leimeining teipaw hratah a cang.
\v 8 Ma hminghring sangpalipaw cawh mathlaw sangruh cacy aa hnui, aa pungpaluh cawh mehkho tah aa mathlaw rai tai zong a chih. Mataico,
\q1 “Abuipaw Khazing Zezong Tuatu,
\q2 a ung ciapaw le a ung leimeipaw le a ung lepaw cawh,
\q1 a pathai, a pathai, a pathai,”
\m tatah ching le zai a hia lytah aa tah.
\v 9 Ma hminghring sangpali sahlo taco, abui dyching letei a typaw, chaizaw tei a hring paria thlangpaw cawh aa parungnawsah, aa upah, lunglawngnah bia zong aa hlai.
\v 10 Ma hratei aa tuaning maikaw tah macang paki le papali sahlo taco, abui dyching letei a typaw a hme letaco aa khuh panai he ka, chaizaw tah chaizaw tai a hringpaw cawh aa beh.
\q1 
\v 11 “Nama, kaa Buipaw le kaa Khazing cawh rungnawnah le
\q2 pasungpanawnah le hmingtuakhynah vytei cawh a hnui tlangpaw na cang.
\q1 Zemaw tah pawco nama tah zezong vytei tua ceh ka,
\q2 na dupaw hratah a va chuhpaw a cang he,” tah he ka,
\q2 aa builukhu zong cawh abui dyching hme letaco aa chia.
\c 5
\s1 Cabu lingpaw le Tuu teitei
\p 
\v 1 Taico abui dyching letei a typaw a cacang lang kih letaco cabu lingpaw sangkheh, a chunglang le alailang letei cia ciapaw, cakhainah sangsarih tei khai ciapaw khah ka hmuh.
\v 2 Taico vaiming a thawtlung ngeteipaw taco, o thang ngeteipaw tah, “Ahomaw ma cakhai vytei heh thlang tah cabu lingpaw heh a hong tlangpaw a ung?” tatah tlang a ypaw khah ka hmuh.
\v 3 Mataico, vaicung letah le alui letah le alui rai letah zong ma cabu lingpaw cawh a hong khypaw le a chunglang a ming khypaw ahohmai ung bei he.
\v 4 Taico, ma cabu cawh hong tah a chunglang a ming tlangpaw ahohmai aa ung ly cawtah ka nge pachia ka, thaw tah ka cah.
\v 5 Taico, macang sahlo hrong letei pakheh taco ka hai letah, “Cah kheh, nawthlia tua, Judah phing Cakebarung, David Thahrangpui a cangpaw taco, ma cabu cawh hong rua pawtah le a cakhainah vytei cawh thlangthlah rua pawtah tenah a lah myca,” tatah a pa tah.
\p 
\v 6 Taico, abui dyching le hminghring sangpali le macang sahlo aa lele taco, Tuu teitei thaw ciapaw a lopaw, ki sangsarih le mehkho sangsarih a hnuipaw a daw thlangpaw cawh ka hmuh. Ma meh sangsarih sahlo cawh Khazing thlawpaw sangsarih, aluicung vytei letei tawchuapaw sahlo cawh a cang he.
\v 7 Ama cawh a vong ka, abui dyching letei a typaw a kih cacang lang letei a ungpaw cabu lingpaw cawh a lah.
\v 8 Mataico, ma cabu lingpaw cawh a lah cangkawleh hminghring sangpali le macang paki le papali cawh Tuu teitei hme leco a bawh he. Pakheh cy tah tingtang le ringthopaw tei a chihpaw sui tuithei cawh a tle cy he. Ma ringthopaw cawh mehpathai sahlo aa thlawchangnah a cang.
\v 9 Taico,
\q1 “Nama cawh cabu lingpaw cawh lá tah
\q2 a cakhai vytei zong a thlang tlangpaw na cang.
\q1 Zecawtamaw tatah thaw ciapaw na cang thah,
\q2 citing, reiting, phingting, raangting leteipaw cawh
\q2 Khazing cawtah na thisai tah co ceh ka,
\q1 
\v 10 kaa Khazing cawtah raihre pawtah tlangbui sahlo le a painah raang cawh na tua he,
\q2 taico, ma alui lehei uhtu a cang he a,”
\m tatah hlaw thapaw aa sah.
\p 
\v 11 Mataico a hui neh ka, a thongsang tah a cangpaw he thonghraw a leh thonghraw a cangpaw he vaiming hlupui o khah ka thui. Vaiming sahlo taco, abui dyching le hminghring sahlo le macang sahlo khah aa cadung thlang he.
\q1 
\v 12 “Thawpaw Tuu teitei cawh hmingtuakhynah le hnuirungnah le
\q1 singnah le chongnah le upahnah le rungnawnah le reithainah khah
\q1 hmuh rua tah a tlahpaw a cang,”
\m tatah o thangpui tah hlaw aa sah.
\p 
\v 13 Mataico, vaicung letei a ungpaw tuapaw maikaw le alui leteipaw maikaw le alui rai leteipaw maikaw le rili leteipaw maikaw le ma sahlo letei a ungpaw vytei sahlo takhei,
\q1 “Buidyching letei a typaw le Tuu teitei khaco
\q2 reithainah le pasungpanawnah le rungnawnah le
\q1 hmingtuakhynah cawh chaizaw tah
\q2 chaizaw tai ung ky seh,”
\m tatah hlaw aa sahpaw ka thui.
\v 14 Hminghring sangpali taco, “Amen,” tatah aa tah. Mataico macang paki le papali sahlo taco aa khuh panai he ka, aa beh.
\c 6
\s1 Cakhai sahlo
\p 
\v 1 Taico, Tuu teitei tah cakhai sangsarih letei a hmetaw caipaw a honghlypaw khah hmuh neh ka, mataico hminghring sangpali letei sangkheh takhei khalung hratah o thangpui tah, “A vong,” a tahpaw khah ka thui.
\v 2 A hui neh ka, ka hme letah rang arangpaw sangkheh ka hmuh. A ketupaw cawh li le thae a tle ka, builukhu sangkheh peh a cang, taico tetupaw tah te rua pawtah a pachiapaw hrakhei a tho.
\p 
\v 3 Tuu teitei tah cakhai a sanghningnah cawh a hong tihtah hminghring a sanghningnah taco, “A vong,” a tahpaw khah ka thui.
\v 4 Mataico ahringpaw rang ka pia ka, me hratah asaipaw a cang. A ketupaw cawh alui letei denah lahly rua pawtah le cawngsaw sahlo pakheh le pakheh a thaw a nawngsah ruapaw takhei hmingtuakhynah peh a cang. Ama cawh zyzi alaipaw pui peh a cang.
\p 
\v 5 Tuu teitei tah cakhai a sangthungnah a hong tihtah hminghring a sangthungnah tah, “A vong,” a tahpaw khah ka thui. A hui neh ka, ka hme letei a ungpaw cawh rang vawngpaw a cang. A ketupaw cawh cuithlenah khah a kih letah a tle.
\v 6 Mataico hminghring sangpali hrong taiteipaw o a lopaw tah, “Ningkheh nihlo tah changvuh cawh pongthung, hrangsang cawh pongkua cypaw cang ka, sathy le misurhang cawh rawh khe o,” a tahpaw khah ka thui.
\p 
\v 7 Tuu teitei tah cakhai a sangpalinah cawh a hong tihtah hminghring a sangpalinah tah, “A vong,” a tahpaw khah ka thui.
\v 8 A hui neh ka, ka hme letei a ungpaw cawh rang paraphu a cang. A cung letah a kepaw cawh Thihnah tatah a mingsah he ka, Mehthi khua takhei a hninglang tah a pazui lai. Aaning cawh alui chypali chykheh cung lekhei zyzi tah le cakaang tah le ruhanah a rawrungpaw le sawhrang sahlo tei thawnah hmingtuakhynah khah peh a cang he.
\p 
\v 9 Mataico, cakhai sangpangawnah khah Tuu teitei tah a hong tihtah Khazing bia rawng tah le a tuapaw a dawkhuinah rawng tei thawpaw sahlo aa thlawpaw khah dangnah siasang rai lekhei ka hmuh he.
\v 10 Taico a thangpui tah y he ka, “A pathaipaw le a hmuisuipaw a cangpaw uhtu Buipaw, alui a pahrangpaw cawngsaw sahlo heh zetih tai maw biacepah lytah ung he ceh ka, kaa thisai phuhlang lytah na ung a?” aa tahpaw ka thui.
\v 11 Mataico aaning cawh pai rangpaw zing kheh cy tah peh cang he ka, “A cawngpe heh cong thlang o, naaning hratei thaw a cangpaw he rai naa hrehruipaw sahlo le naa uny sahlo tling balang bei he,” tatah a ching he.
\p 
\v 12 Taico, cakhai a sangruhnah khah Tuu teitei tah a hongpaw khah hmuh neh ka, mataico aling a rupui tah a hrui. Taico ning cawh mei hming tei tuapaw buri pai hrakhei a vawngpaw tah a tua ka, thlawpaw cawh thisai hrakhei asai.
\v 13 Mataico, thuiku kung khah thlipui tah a calawh ning tah thuiku a zungpaw hrakhei avai esi cawh alui lang a tlah thlu he.
\v 14 Avai cawh cabu lingpaw hrakhei a ling ka, tlaang le tuiraw raang maikaw cawh aa hminghmaw taikhei a palong thlu he.
\p 
\v 15 Mataico alui siangpahrang sahlo, abui sawcapaw sahlo, raebui sahlo, mehrung sahlo, mehthawtlung sahlo le sae maikaw le mehlua maikaw cawh tlaang sahlo letei alung hrong letah le lungkua lekhei a nawh he.
\v 16 Taico, tlaang sahlo le alung sahlo khah y he ka, “A ma liaso la, buidyching letei a typaw mehmuh le Tuu teitei a thingaenah taikhei ma pakhang tua o!
\v 17 Zecawtamaw tatah a thingaenah ning rawrung a ungpaw cawh va chuh myca ka, ahomaw a cae a?” tatah aa tah.
\c 7
\s1 144,000 cakhai a cang he
\p 
\v 1 Ma khy taico alui ki kipali letah vaiming papali a daw thlangpaw he khah hmuh he neh ka, aaning taco alui kipali letei thli khah raang letah cang seh, rili letah cang seh, thingkung cung letah cang seh a hrang ly nápaw he takhei aa tlepakhih he.
\v 2 Mataico, Khazing hring cakhai a tlepaw ahringpaw vaiming khah nichualang tah a vongpaw khah ka hmuh. Ama taco alui le rili hanah peh ruapaw tei hmingtuakhynah peh a cangpaw he vaiming papali khah a thangpui tah a y he,
\v 3 “Alui le rili le thingkung sahlo cawh kaa Khazing a sae sahlo aa pangcarih letah cakhai kaa khai hlai taco hanah pei balang khe o,” tatah a tah he.
\v 4 Mataico cakhai a cangpaw sahlo cawh khazeh maw a cang tah cawh ka thui. Israel mingphing vytei taitah 144,000 a cang he.
\v 5 Judah phing taitah 12,000. Reuben phing taitah 12,000. Gad phing taitah 12,000.
\v 6 Asher phing taitah 12,000. Naftali phing taitah 12,000. Manaseh phing taitah 12,000.
\v 7 Simeon phing taitah 12,000. Levi phing taitah 12,000. Isakhar phing taitah 12,000.
\v 8 Zebulun phing taitah 12,000. Josef phing taitah 12,000. Benjamin phing taitah 12,000 a cang he.
\s1 Pai rang a buhpaw cawngsaw rungpui
\p 
\v 9 Ma khy taico ming neh ka, ka hme letei a ungpaw he cawh buidyching hme le Tuu teitei hme letei a daw thlangpaw he, raangting, citing le phing ting le rei ting taitah a va chuh pawhe reite a cang lypaw cawngsaw rungpui khah ka hmuh he. Pai rang khah a buh he ka, aa kih letah tung ky a tle thlang he.
\v 10 Taico a thangpui tah y he ka,
\q1 “Pachahnah cawh buidyching cung letei
\q1 a typaw kaa Khazing le
\q1 Tuu teitei tei a cang,”
\m tatah aa tah.
\m 
\v 11 Vaiming vytei takhei buidyching le macang sahlo le hminghring sangpali khah a daw cahlung he ka, taico buidyching hme lekhei aa khuh panai tah a bung he ka, Khazing khah aa beh,
\q1 
\v 12 “Amen!
\q1 Reithainah le rungnawnah le
\q1 singnah le alawngnah le pasungpanawnah le
\q1 hmingtuakhynah le chongnah cawh
\q1 kaa Khazing khatah
\q1 chaizaw tah chaizaw tai ung ky seh, Amen!”
\m tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 13 Mataico, macang letei pakheh takhei, “Ma pai rang a buhpaw sahlo heh aho sahlo maw aa cang? Zelang tamaw aa va chua?” tatah a pa hae.
\p 
\v 14 “Ka pu, nama tah pui na hni kata,” tatah ka chai.
\p Mataico ama taco, “Ma tlaw heh cawh taithuinah alaipaw pui ingnah taitei a ka piachuapaw cang he ka, Tuu teitei thisai letah aa pai khah suh he ka, aa pai cawh a raangsah myca he.
\v 15 Macawtaco,
\q1 Khazing buidyching hme letah ung he ka,
\q2 a behnah ing letah ching kha, zai kha a rai aa hre,
\q1 taico buidyching letah a typaw takhei a thlangda khah aa cung letah a pakai pá he a.
\q1 
\v 16 Aa ngaidi khawh by be,
\q2 aa tui hrae khawh by be,
\q1 ningsaw tah ry khawh be ca he ka,
\q2 sehu sehe tah ung khaw bei he.
\q1 
\v 17 Zecawtamaw tatah buidyching a lecingcing letei a typaw,
\q2 Tuu teitei takhei aaning cawh king he ka, Ama taco aaning cawh hringnah tuihnaw lang khah a hrui he.
\q1 Taico Khazing tah aa meh letei aa mehthli vytei cawh a hruhly pá he a,”
\m tatah a tah.
\c 8
\s1 Cakhai sangsarihnah le sui kangphae
\p 
\v 1 Cakhai sangsarihnah khah Tuu teitei tah a hong tihtah vaicung leco suimehlang a chy a calinah a ung.
\p 
\v 2 Taico, Khazing hme letah a dawpaw he vaiming pasarih hmuh he neh ka, aaning cawh hmoka sangsarih khah peh a cang he.
\p 
\v 3 Ahringpaw vaiming, sui kangphae a hnuipaw cawh a vong ka, dangnah siasang letah a daw ka, buidyching hme letei a ungpaw dangnah sui siasang cung lekhei mehpathai sahlo thlawchangnah khatei hlai ruapaw takhei sathy ringthopaw a hlupui khah peh a cang.
\v 4 Mataico sathy ringthopaw khu cawh mehpathai sahlo thlawchangnah khakhei hmokheh tah vaiming kih taico Khazing hme letah a ka khu chy.
\v 5 Mataico vaiming taco kangphae lekhei dangnah siasang letei me khah chih ky tah dui ka, alui lang a heihly. Taico khalung a thih, o va ring ka, lailaw ky ka, aling a hrui.
\s1 Hmoka sahlo
\p 
\v 6 Mataico vaiming pasarih sahlo takhei aa hmoka sangsarih khah tung a pachia he.
\p 
\v 7 Vaiming a pakhehnah tah a hmoka khah tung ka, aria le me, thisai kha a pahlawhpaw ka pia ka, ma cawh alui lang va thlah a cang. Taico alui chythung chykheh khah kang ka, thingkung chythung chykheh khah kang thlu ka, araang ahringpaw vytei khah a kang thlu he.
\p 
\v 8 Vaiming a pahningnah tah a hmoka cawh a tung tihtah me a hla thluama leimeipaw tlaang alaipaw pui hapaw cawh rili lang va thlah a cang. Taico rili khah chythung chykheh cawh thisai tah a tua ka,
\v 9 rili letei a ungpaw hminghring chythung chykheh cawh thi he ka, tuilawng chythung chykheh cawh a rawhrang thlu he.
\p 
\v 10 Mataico, vaiming a pathungnah tah a hmoka khah a tung tihtah dame hratah akhaipaw esi alaipaw pui cawh avai taitah tuivaw chythung chykheh le tuikho cung lekhei a za tlah.
\v 11 Ma esi cawh a ming tah, “Akheh,” aa tah. Taico tui chythung chykheh cawh akhehpaw tah a tua he ka, ma akhehpaw tei a tuapaw tui a dingpaw cawngsaw hlupui cawh a thi thlu he.
\p 
\v 12 Vaiming a papalinah tah a hmoka khah a tung tihtah ning chythung chykheh, thlawpaw chythung chykheh le esi chythung chykheh cawh a calawh he ka, ma chythung chykheh sahlo cawh a mui thlu he, taico ching chythung chykheh cawh khai lytah ung he ka, zai chythung chykheh zong khai hrah bei heh.
\p 
\v 13 Ka ming thlang chung taco, avai letei a zythi leimeipaw pahmupui cawh a thangpui tah saang ka, “Aa cing a ping! Aa cing a ping! Alui a pahrangpaw sahlo cawh aa cing a ping, zemaw tah pawco, ahringpaw vaiming pathung tah aa tung lepaw hmoka o rawng takhei a cang,” a tahpaw khah ka thui.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Vaiming a papangawnah tah a hmoka khah a tung tihtah avai taitah alui lang esi sangkheh a tlahpaw khah ka hmuh. Taico, ma esi cawh a ping thai lypaw mehthi khua khobatlung cabi khah peh a cang.
\v 2 Mehthi khua khobatlung cawh a hong tihtah mepho alaipaw pui taitei mekhu hapaw mekhu khah a ka pia, taico mehthi khua khobatlung taiteipaw mekhu taco ning le avai khah a pa zing he.
\v 3 Mataico mekhu taico khybawh sahlo cawh ka pia he ka, alui lang a za tlah he. Taico khybawh sahlo cawh alui letei thingca-e tah hmingtuakhynah a hnuipaw hratah hmingtuakhynah cawh peh a cang he.
\v 4 Aaning sahlo cawh si le raang sahlo le thingkung sahlo cawh rawh khe o, a cang naná tah aa pangcarih letah Khazing cakhai a hnui lypaw longlong naa ro he tatah aa ching he.
\v 5 Mataico, aaning sahlo khah thaw ruapaw takhei khybawh sahlo cawh hmingtuakhynah peh cang bei he, canghrasala thlah pangaw chung naa hrai he tah a cang he. Taico aa ingpaw asawnah cawh thingca-e a lahme a pazopaw tei cawngsaw a ching tihtah a sawpaw hrakhei a cang.
\v 6 Ma ningcai leco cawngsaw sahlo takhei thihnah khah aa hui a, canghrasala hmuh a bei he. Thih khah aa du ngetei a, canghrasala thihnah takhei a nosai he a.
\p 
\v 7 Ma khybawh sahlo cawh raetuhnah caw tei pachiapaw rang sahlo khah aa lo. Aa lu letah suilukhu hapaw khah a khusah he ka, aa hme cawh cawngsaw hme aa lo.
\v 8 Mataico aa sang cawh canu sang hrakhei cang ka, aa haw cawh cakebarung haw hrakhei a cang.
\v 9 Kangpathi pho hapaw aa cacanghnaw letah a bai he ka, aa mathlaw py cawh raetuhnah hming lang a saipaw rang sahlo le ranglai sahlo khalung aa pathih thlangpaw py ky a lo.
\v 10 Mataico thingca-e hrakhei ahling chipaw lahme hnui he ka, aa lahme lekhei thlah pangaw chung cawngsaw hrai khynah hmingtuakhynah aa hnui.
\v 11 Mataico aa cung lekhei abui hnui he ka, ama cawh mehthi khua khobatlung a uhtu vaiming khah cang ka, a ming cawh Hebru rei tah Abadon tah he ka, Grik rei tah Apolion aa tah. A silang cawh Rawhrangtu tahnah a cang.
\p 
\v 12 Cingpingnah a sangkhehnah cawh a khung myca. Ahringpaw cingpingnah sanghning cawh a va chuh vy he a.
\p 
\v 13 Vaiming a paruhnah tah a hmoka khah a tung tihtah Khazing hme letei dangnah sui siasang letei sawki kipali taikhei o a ringpaw khah ka thui.
\v 14 Ma o taco hmoka a hnuipaw vaiming a paruhnah khah, “Zufreti tuivaw puino letei tongchaipaw vaiming papali khah papia o,” tatah a tah.
\v 15 Mataico, ma kung le ma thlaw le ma ning le ma suimehlang cai lelei lehei, mehnung chythung chykheh khah thaw ruapaw tei a mai pacia tei ung sahpaw vaiming papali cawh papia a cang he.
\v 16 Rang raekeh cawh thongzahning a leh thongzakheh a cang he. Ma cawh ka thuipaw zeh cawh a cang.
\p 
\v 17 Ma apalynah leco rang sahlo le a cipaw sahlo ka hmuh he. Aa cacanghnaw a pachawngkhainah pho cawh asaipaw me hratah le avongcakupaw le kaa hratah amaipaw a cang he. Rang sahlo aa lu cawh cakebarung lu lo he ka, aa kaw taitah me, mekhu le kaa aa pia he.
\v 18 Mehnung chythung chykheh cawh aa kaw taitei a piapaw ruhanah rawrungpaw phingthung a cangpaw he, me le mekhu le kaa tahpaw sahlo khei thaw a cang he.
\v 19 Rang sahlo aa hmingtuakhynah cawh aa kaw le aa lahme lekhei a ung, zecawtamaw tatah aa lahme cawh pari hratah lu hnui he ka, aa lahme co mehnung khah a sawsah he.
\p 
\v 20 Ma ruhanah rawrungpaw tei a thawbangpaw he cawngsaw sahlo cawh aa kiá tei suanah aa tuapaw hming khah chi hlui bei he. Khachia, sui nono, ngung nono, daa nono, alung nono, thing nono khua a hmuh lypaw, khua a thui lypaw, a seithai lypaw beh khah tai hlui bei he.
\v 21 Lee aa nongnah, ca-ia aa thainah le canu capaw suanah aa tuapaw le aa ruh thainah zong khah a ngepachih bei he.
\c 10
\s1 Vaiming le cabu lingpaw a chia pawtei
\p 
\v 1 Mataico, ahringpaw a thawtlungpaw vaiming vaicung taitah a za cungpaw khah hmuh neh ka, ama cawh meding khah a hrei. A lu cung letah mesakupaw a zaang ka, a hme cawh ning lo ka, a ngaelang cawh metung aa lo.
\v 2 Ama cawh a kih letah a pakai thlangpaw cabu lingpaw a chia pawtei khah a tle ka, a cacang lang phe khei rili khah tlai ka, a cavui lang phe khei alui khah a tlai.
\v 3 Taico, cakebarung a hrungpaw hrakhei a thangpui tah a y. A hrung khy taico khalung sangsarih o tah bia aa rei.
\v 4 Taico, khalung sangsarih o tah bia a reining taco, ca tah ka cia a tah neh ka, canghrasala vaicung taitah, “Khalung sangsarih bia khah cakhai khai la, cia balang kheh,” tatah a pa tahpaw o ka thui.
\p 
\v 5 Mataico, rili le alui a cung letei a daw thlangpaw vaiming ka hmuhpaw taco, a cacang lang kih cawh vaicung lang khah a calia.
\v 6 Taico, chaizaw tah chaizaw tai a hringpaw, avai le a chung leteipaw vytei a papipaw, alui le a chung leteipaw vytei a papipaw le rili le a chung leteipaw vytei a papipaw Khazing ming khei chia a sah ka, “Ry khaw be!
\v 7 Canghrasala vaiming a pasarihnah tah a hmoka khah a tung tih taco, Khazing tah a sae khuavang sahlo hai letei a za reipaw hrakhei Khazing biaparuh cawh a tling a,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 8 Mataico, vaicung letei ka thuipaw o takhei bia pa ching kaw hui ka, “Va sei la, rili le alui khah tlai katei, a daw thlangpaw vaiming a kih letei a pakai thlangpaw cabu lingpaw a chia pawtei khah va law,” tatah a pa tah.
\p 
\v 9 Macawtaco vaiming khaco a vaw neh ka, cabu lingpaw cawh pa pei law tatah ka va tah. Ama taco, “Law la, e. Na ri leco a thobahla a, canghrasala na kaw leco akhui tui hratah a thlung a,” tatah a pa tah.
\v 10 Vaiming a kih letei cabu lingpaw a chia pawtei cawh law neh ka, ka e. Ka kaw leco akhui tui hratah a thlung, canghrasala ka lang tihtah ka ri leco a thobahla.
\v 11 Mataico, “Mingphing hlupui, raang hlupui, rei hlupui le siangpahrang hlupui sahlo kong letei Khazing tah a reipaw bia khah na rei hry kaw a,” tatah a pa tah.
\c 11
\s1 Hnikhuitu pahning
\p 
\v 1 Nehnah basung a lopaw phepahla kung kung kheh pa pei ka, “Va sei la, Khazing behnah ing le dangnah siasang khah va neh la, ma letei Khazing a behpaw sahlo khah va rei tua o.
\v 2 Canghrasala alailang letei dungkalung kheh cawh va reipai kheh la, va neh kheh, zecawtamaw tatah ma kheh cawh Khazing a zing lypaw Gental cawngsaw sahlo pehpaw he a cang. Aaning sahlo taco a pathaipaw khuapui cawh thlawpaw thlah songli le thlahning chung aa phe tah aa tlaichai a.
\v 3 Taico kama a pa hnikhuitu pahning khah hmingtuakhynah pei he neh ka, buri khah a hrei he ka, aaning taco, ning 1260 chung bia aa phy a,” tatah a pa ching.
\v 4 Ma cawngsaw tlaw heh alui Buipaw a hme letei a dawpaw oliv kung hning le me-ing chianah tung tunghning cawh a cang he.
\v 5 Taico, ahotahmai tah aaning cawh hanah peh a pachia caco he, aa kaw taitah me piá ka, aa carae cawh a kangseh he a. Ahohmai aaning hanah peh a pachiapaw sahlo cawh Khazing tah ma hrahei a thaw he a.
\v 6 Ma cawngsaw sahlo heh cawh bia aa phy chung vytei khua kangsah khynah hmingtuakhynah hnui he ka, aa duning cai maikaw tah tui khah thisai cangsah khynah le alui khah ruhanah rawrungpaw a phingphing tah hrai khynah hmingtuakhynah zong aa hnui.
\p 
\v 7 Hnikhuinah bia aa reipaw aa pachang khy taitah a chang thai lypaw mehthi khua khobatlung chung taitah a kapiapaw sawhrang takhei zonghno he ka, te he ka, a thaw he a.
\v 8 Aa rawh cawh alaipaw khuapui langpui lekhei a lia thlang a. Ma khuapui leco aa Buipaw khah khraws letah khaipai a cang. Ma khuapui cawh a suanah le a pialuinah cawtah thlawpaw lang ming co, Sodom khua le Izipt raang tah a cang.
\v 9 Phingting, citing, reiting le raangting taitei cawngsaw takhei aa rawh cawh ningthung le a chy ming he ka, aa rawh phung cawh ahohmai sai cang bei he.
\v 10 Alui a pahrangpaw sahlo cawh alawngnah tua he ka, aa thaw a chah tu cawtah khei pakheh le pakheh lahsong a pei he a, zecawtamaw tatah ma Khazing khuavang pahning tahei aluicung letah a ungpaw sahlo khah taithui ngetei tah aa tuanah caw he tah a cang.
\p 
\v 11 Canghrasala, ningthung le a chy khy tah Khazing taitei hringnah hu cawh aaning kha a nae ka, a daw he ka, a hmuhpaw sahlo cawh aa ci a tho.
\v 12 Mataico, o thangpui tei vaicung taitah, “Ma lang heh a khong o,” a tahpaw khah aa thui. Taico, aa carae sahlo tei aa cai thlangning he takhei, meding co avai lang khah aa seichy.
\p 
\v 13 Ma cai lalei leco aling a rupaw pui a hrui ka, khuapui chyhraw chykheh cawh a rawh. Ma aling a hruinah leco cawngsaw 7000 thi he ka, a tangpaw cawh ci tu he ka, vaicung Khazing khah rungnawnah aa peh.
\p 
\v 14 Cingpingnah sanghningnah cawh a khung myca, sangthungnah a va chuh palang a.
\s1 Hmoka sangsarihnah
\p 
\v 15 Vaiming a pasarihnah takhei a hmoka cawh tung ka, vaicung lekhei o thangpui tah a ringpaw taco,
\q1 “Khazaw painah raang cawh kaa Buipaw le a Khri painah raang tah cang myca ka,
\q2 Ama taco chaizaw tah chaizaw tai a uh myca a,”
\m tatah aa tah.
\v 16 Taico, macang paki le papali, Khazing hme letei aa buidyching letah a typaw sahlo cawh a bung hmotah aa khuh panai he ka, Khazing khah aa beh.
\q1 
\v 17 “Abuipaw Khazing Zezong Tuatu, alawngnah bia kaa ca hlai,
\q2 Nama cawh a ung leimeipaw le a ung thahpaw na cang,
\q1 zecawtamaw tatah a rungnaw ngeteipaw na hmingtuakhynah khah
\q2 law ceh ka, uhnah hrang na patho myca.
\q1 
\v 18 Raang sahlo cawh aa thingae ka, na thing a tho myca hrah, mehthi biacenah cai le na sae,
\q2 Khazing khuavang sahlo le mehpathai sahlo le na ming a cizawpaw sahlo,
\q1 mehlai kha mehchia kha lahsong pehnah cai
\q2 le alui a rawhrangpaw sahlo he hlydenah cai cawh a tlung myca,”
\m tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 19 Mataico, vaicung letei Khazing behnah ing cawh a hong ka, a behnah ing chung letei pasungpanaw ngeteipaw biahrai thingkawng cawh a lang. Mataico lailaw a ky, o a va ring, khalung a thih, aling a hrui ka, aria alaipaw pui a tlah.
\c 12
\s1 Canu le paribui
\p 
\v 1 Khuarawha chuipaw paching pakhanah alaipaw pui sangkheh cawh avai letah a va lang. Canu pakheh cawh ning a hrei ka, thlawpaw cawh a phe rai letah ung ka, a lu letah esi sanghrawhluihning lukhu tah a khu.
\v 2 Ama cawh sawtei pho ka, a chai zaa ka, ny ung risaw khei a ysang.
\v 3 Mataico, ahringpaw paching pakhanah a cangpaw paribui asaipaw alai ngeteipaw, lusarih hnui katei, a ki kihraw a hnuipaw, a lu maikaw letah builukhu a khupaw cawh avai letah a va lang.
\v 4 A lahme tah avai letei esi chythung chykheh khah cakhia hly he ka, alui lang a za thlah he. Taico, ma paribui cawh a chai a zapaw canuno a sawtei cawh a za pi cangkawleh e pawtah canuno a hme leco a daw thlang.
\v 5 Ma canu cawh mingphing vytei khah thaw cungcahrei tah a uh ruapaw he tah sawcapaw khah a sah. Taico a sawcapaw cawh pazah pahraw he ka, Khazing le a buidyching lang khah seikhui a cang.
\v 6 Canuno cawh Khazing tah ning 1260 chung mingkhai rua pawtah a pachia thahpaw raangcaa lang khah a sai.
\p 
\v 7 Taico vaicung letah rae a tho. Mikhal le a vaiming sahlo tah paribui khah dy he ka, paribui le a vaiming sahlo takhei aa dy hri hrah he.
\v 8 Canghrasala paribui tah te be ca he ka, ama le a vaiming sahlo cawh vaicung taitah aa nangthlah he.
\v 9 Paribui alaipaw pui cawh heihly a cang. Ma paribui cawh khuahlai paribui, khachia a cang ly leh Setan tahpaw khah cang ka, khazaw pungpaluh lang a pavesah paw khah a cang. Ama le a vaiming sahlo cawh alui lang khah heihly a cang he.
\p 
\v 10 Mataico vaicung letah,
\q1 “Kaa Khazing pachahnah le hmingtuakhynah le painah le
\q2 a Khri nawhnuinah cawh atoheh a tling myca,
\q1 zecawtamaw tatah kaa uny sahlo sua a putu he,
\q2 ching le zai tah kaa Khazing hmekaw letei sua a putu he cawh heihly a cang myca.
\q1 
\v 11 Tuu teitei thihnah thisai thongtah le a dawkhuinah pawhe bia thongtah
\q2 aaning sahlo taco, ama cawh aa te myca.
\q1 Aa hringnah peh zong sai he ka,
\q2 thih zong aa ngang.
\q1 
\v 12 Macawtaco naaning vaicung sahlo le a chung letei a ungpaw sahlo,
\q2 a lawng myca o!
\q1 Canghrasala, alui le rili cawh naa cing a ping,
\q2 zemaw tah pawco Setan cawh naaning khatah a tlahthlah myca!
\q1 Ama cawh a thing a ling tah a paling thlang,
\q2 zecawtamaw tatah cai a cawngpe long ka hnui takhah a hni cawtah a cang,”
\m tatah tahpaw o khah ka thui.
\p 
\v 13 Paribui taco alui lang heihly ka cang myca takhah a hni tihtah sawcapaw a sahpaw canuno khah a cadai.
\v 14 Canuno cawh raangcaa letei aa pachia pahpaw hminghmaw lang a zy nápawtah pahmupui a mathlaw sanghning khah peh cang ka, ma leco kung thung le a chy mingkai cang ka, paribui taco phah khy be.
\v 15 Mataico, paribui taco canuno cawh phohly ná seh tah ka, a kaw taitah tuivaw hratah tui a phuhly.
\v 16 Canghrasala alui taco canuno cawh a baw ka, a kaw ang ka, paribui tei a kaw taitah a papiapaw tuivaw tui khah a lang thlu.
\v 17 Mataico, paribui cawh canuno cung leco a thingae ngetei ka, canuno a pathlah a tangpaw sahlo, Khazing biapeh nge he katei, Zisu a dawkhuipaw sahlo he khah rae dy rua pawtah a piathlah.
\c 13
\s1 Rili taitah a kapiapaw sawhrang
\p 
\v 1 Taico, paribui cawh rili ngaekang lekhei a daw thlang ka, taico rili taitah sawhrang a kapiapaw khah ka hmuh. Ama cawh ki kihraw le lu lusarih hnui ka, a ki letah builukhu sanghraw a khu, taico a lu maikaw lekhei Khazing reipachianah ming khah a cia.
\v 2 Ma sawhrang cawh cake ketei a lo, canghrasala a phe cawh cavong phe lo ka, a hmo cawh cakebarung hmo a lo. Paribui taco, ma sawhrang cawh a hmingtuakhynah khah le abui dyching le nawhnuinah alaipaw pui cawh a peh.
\v 3 Ma sawhrang a lu lukheh cawh thih khuipaw hmaw za pho bang seh la khatah a nge, canghrasala, ma a thihkhui khypaw hmaw cawh a dang thah. Khazaw pungpaluh cawh aa khuarawh haa ka, ma sawhrang cawh aa zui.
\v 4 Aaning tah ma paribui cawh aa beh, zecawtamaw tatah sawhrang khah nawhnuinah a peh rawng tah cang ka, sawhrang zong cawh beh he ka, “Sawhrang a lopaw ahomaw a ung? Ahomaw ama dy rua tah rae a tho khy a?” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 5 Sawhrang cawh a palai a patuinah bia le Khazing reipachianah biareinah naw khah peh cang ka, thlawpaw thlah songli le thlahning chung a nawhnuinah hmang pawtah peh a cang.
\v 6 Khazing khah reipachia ka, a ming le a ungnahpaw hminghmaw le vaicung letei a ungpaw sahlo khah a pachia a pahru thlu he.
\v 7 Raetho tah mehpathai sahlo dy rua tah le te rua pawtah ama cawh hmingtuakhynah khah peh a cang. Taico citing, phingting, reiting le raangting cung letah nawhnuinah khah peh a cang he.
\v 8 Thaw ciapaw Tuu teitei hringnah cabu letei khazaw tua thoning taitei ming cia lypaw, alui a pahrangpaw vytei tah sawhrang cawh aa beh a.
\p 
\v 9 Thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco thui he seh.
\q1 
\v 10 Thong a tlah ruapaw a cangpaw sahlo cawh
\q2 thongtlah thlang ky he seh.
\q1 Zyzi tei thaw ruapaw aa cangpaw sahlo cawh
\q2 zyzi tah thaw cang ky he seh.
\m Ma lehei mehpathai sahlo cawh lungsy tah ingkhynah le zingchuinah aa hnuipaw cawh aa palang a hy.
\s1 Alui taitei a piapaw sawhrang
\p 
\v 11 Mataico ahringpaw sawhrang, alui taitah a kapiapaw khah ka hmuh. Ama cawh tuu teitei ki a lopaw ki sanghning a hnui, canghrasala paribui hratah bia a rei.
\v 12 Sawhrang hmetawpaw nawhnuinah vytei khah sawhrang hmetawpaw vypaw tah hmang ka, alui a pahrangpaw sahlo cawh thih khuipaw hmaw a phopaw dangsah a cang kawpaw sawhrang khah a behsah he.
\v 13 Taico, cawngsaw sahlo mehmuh letah avai taitah alui lang me tlahsah khynah, khuarawha chuipaw paching pakhanah alaipui khah a tua.
\v 14 Ama tah cawngsaw khah a dungkhei he, zecawtamaw tatah ama cawh sawhrang hmetawpaw cai takhei paching pakhanah tua pawtah hmingtuakhynah khah peh a cang. Zyzi tei hmaw pho katei, a thi lypaw sawhrang hmetawpaw upahnah cawtah khei ama kha a lopaw nono naa tua a tatah bia a peh he.
\v 15 Ama cawh nono tah rei a thlaw khy nápawtah hu suanah peh cawh sai a cang. Sawhrang hmuisang a lopaw nono a beh du lypaw maikaw cawh thaw a cang he.
\v 16 Ama taco, ming maikaw alai a chia, mehsisah mehrung, sae le mehlua khah aa cacang lang kih letah a cang ly leh aa pangcarih letah ngianah na tua ceingei a tatah a tah he.
\v 17 Sawhrang a ming, a cang ly leh a ming nambar a cangpaw ngianah a hnui lypaw cawh ahohmai hming co khy a bei he, a zua zong zua khy hra bei he.
\p 
\v 18 Ma lehei singnah hmang a hy. Pakheh kheh tah singnah a hnui caco, sawhrang nambar cawh pacang seh. Zecawtamaw tatah ma heh mehnung pakheh nambar cang ka, ma a nambar cawh 666 a cang.
\c 14
\s1 Tuu teitei le a zuipaw 144,000
\p 
\v 1 Mataico a hui neh ka, Tuu teitei Zion tlaang letei a daw thlangpaw khah ka hmuh. Ama khaco, aa pangcarih letah Ama a ming le a Paw ming a khaipaw cawngsaw 144,000 a ung he.
\v 2 Taico vaicung taitah tuiraso py a lopaw le khalung a thihpaw py a lopaw py khah ka thui. Ka thuipaw py cawh tingtang py ky a lo.
\v 3 Taico aaning sahlo taco buidyching hme letah le hminghring sangpali hme letah le macang sahlo hme lekhei hlaw thapaw khah aa sah. Ma hlaw cawh alui taitei tlangpaw cawngsaw 144,000 tah ly co ahotahmai cawng khy bei he.
\v 4 Ma sahlo heh canu khatei a papia a palui lypaw sahlo a cang he, zecawtamaw tatah a pathai teitah a ung he. Aaning sahlo tahei Tuu teitei a seinah maikaw lang aa zuilai. Ma sahlo heh Khazing le Tuu teitei cawtah thuisu hmetawpaw hratah cawngsaw hrong taitei cawhpaw cang he ka, pehlaipaw a cang he.
\v 5 Aaning cawh hingbia rei bang bei he. Suise aa kawh lypaw a cang he.
\s1 Vaiming pathung
\p 
\v 6 Mataico, avai letei a zy laipaw ahringpaw vaiming pakheh hmuh neh ka, ama cawh alui letei a ungpaw he raangting, citing, reiting le phingting khatah rei ruapaw chaizaw thawngchawbia a hnuipaw a cang.
\v 7 Ama taco o thangpui tah, “Khazing cawh cizaw la, ama cawh parungnaw my lo, zecawtamaw tatah biacenah ningcai a tlung myca. Alui, avai, rili le tuihnaw a tuatupaw cawh beh my lo,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 8 Vaiming a pahningnah tah pazui ka, “A rungnawpaw Babilon khuapui cawh a rawhrang myca! A rawhrang myca! Ama taco raangting khah a hohenah thingaenah misur zu khah a dingsah he,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 9 Vaiming a pathungnah taco pazui he ka, a thangpui tah, “Sawhrang le ama a nono beh katei, a pangcarih letah a cang ly leh a kih letah ama ngianah a hnuipaw,
\v 10 cawngsaw sahlo cawh Khazing thingaenah ny letei tlaipaw misur zu a patahpaw khah aa ding hra a. Aaning cawh vaiming pathai sahlo le Tuu teitei hme lekhei kaa me letah hreh aa cang he a.
\v 11 Mataico, aaning aa hreh pawhe me taitah a chuhpaw mekhu cawh chaizaw tah chaizaw tai a khu leimei thlang a. Sawhrang a cang ly leh a lingthlaw nono beh katei, a ming ngianah a hnuipaw maikaw cawh ching le zai tah a hia bei he,” tatah a tah.
\v 12 Khazing biapeh a ngepaw mehpathai sahlo le Zisu angepainah letei a hming thlangpaw sahlo cawh lungsy tah ingkhynah aa hnui a hy.
\p 
\v 13 Mataico vaicung taitah, “Atoning taitei Abuipaw letei a thipaw sahlo cawh bonghnang aa ting tatah cia,” tahpaw o ka thui.
\p Mataico Thlawpaw tah, “A cang, raisah aa hrenah taitah a hia myca he ka, aa tuasenah takhei a va zui hra he a,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Aluicung sacaang hre
\p 
\v 14 A hui neh ka, ka hme letei a ungpaw meding araangpaw cung leco Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a lopaw cawh a ty thlang ka, abui suilukhu a khu ka, a kih letah sahaw a te ngeteipaw a tle thlangpaw khah ka hmuh.
\v 15 Mataico vaiming ahringpaw cawh behnah ing chung taitah ka pia ka, meding cung letei a tythlangpaw cawh a thangpui tah y ka, “Na sahaw khah a lah la, saang cawh eh myca, zecawtamaw tatah saze hre cai a cang myca, alui letei saze cawh hre a zaw myca he,” tatah a tah.
\v 16 Macawtaco, meding cung letei a tythlangpaw cawngsawpaw taco a sahaw khei alui letei saze khah a hre.
\p 
\v 17 Vaicung behnah ing chung taikhei ahringpaw vaiming cawh ka pia ka, ama zong cawh sahaw a te ngeteipaw khah a hnui hrah.
\v 18 Mataico me cung letah nawhnuitu vaiming ahringpaw cawh dangnah siasang taitah ka pia ka, sahaw a te ngeteipaw a hnuipaw vaiming khah a thangpui tah y ka, “Na sahaw a te ngeteipaw cawh law la, alui letei misur thui sahlo khah a thla pui khei pakhong myca, zecawtamaw tatah misur thui cawh aa hming myca he,” tatah a tah.
\v 19 Vaiming taco a sahaw cawh alui leco thlah ka, misur thui sahlo cawh pakhong he ka, Khazing thingaenah a cangpaw misurhang sonah kho lekhei a tlaihly he.
\v 20 Ma sahlo cawh khuapui khungthing lang a ungpaw misur sonah kho lekhei, aa phe tah ci he ka, misurhang sonah taitei thisai a kapiapaw cawh khang 200 tai lai ka, pei pangaw tluh a thuh.
\c 15
\s1 Ruhanah a rawrungpaw sangsarih
\p 
\v 1 Mataico vaicung lekhei khuarawha a chuipaw paching pakhanah alaipaw ahringpaw khah ka hmuh. Ahning caipaw ruhanah rawrungpaw sangsarih khatei a cangpaw vaiming pasarih khah hmuh he neh ka, ma heh a hningcaipaw cawh a cang, zecawtamaw tatah aaning khahei Khazing thingaenah cawh a tling thah.
\v 2 Taico me khatei pahlawhpaw thlalang rili a lopaw khah hmuh neh ka, sawhrang le ama a lingthlaw le a ming nambar cung letah tenah a hnuitu sahlo khah Khazing tei a pehpaw he tingtang khah a tle he ka, ma rili cung lekhei a daw thlang he.
\v 3 Khazing saecapaw Moses a hlaw le Tuu teitei a hlaw khah aa sah.
\q1 “Abuipaw Khazing Zezong Tuatu,
\q2 na hming tuapaw cawh rungnaw ka, ningang a chui,
\q1 mingphing vytei aa Siangpahrang na langpui cawh
\q2 a dingpaw le a hmuisuipaw a cang.
\q1 
\v 4 Vy Abuipaw, nama a ca ci lypaw le
\q2 na ming rungnawnah a ca pei lypaw cawh ahomaw a cang?
\q1 Zecawtamaw tatah a pathaipaw cawh nama suitei na cang.
\q1 Mingphing vytei a vong he ka,
\q2 na hme letah aa khuh aa panai a,
\q1 zecawtamaw tatah na raihrenah a dingpaw cawh a lang myca,”
\m tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 5 Ma khy taico a hui neh ka, vaicung letei behnah ing, biatainah thingkawng chianahpaw thlangda a cangpaw cawh a honghlypaw khah ka hmuh.
\v 6 Ruhanah rawrungpaw sangsarih khatei a cangpaw vaiming pasarih cawh behnah ing taico a ka pia he. Aaning sahlo cawh a pathaipaw pai le a tlypaw a hrei he ka, aa cacanghnaw letah sui cacanghnaw a tongchainah khah a pazai he.
\v 7 Mataico hminghring sangpali letei pakheh takhei chaizaw tah chaizaw tai ahringpaw Khazing thingaená tah a chihpaw sui kaity sangsarih cawh vaiming pasarih khah a peh he.
\v 8 Taico, behnah ing cawh Khazing rungnawnah mekhu le a hmingtuakhynah mekhu khei chih ka, vaiming pasarih tah ruhanah rawrungpaw sangsarih aa tlung sahpaw a chang hlai vytei cawh behnah ing chunglang ahohmai a nae khy bei he.
\c 16
\s1 Khazing thingaenah kaity sangsarih
\p 
\v 1 Mataico behnah ing taikhei vaiming pasarih khah, “Va sei la, Khazing thingaenah kaity sangsarih khah alui letah va tlaihly o,” tatah a thangpui tah a tahpaw he khah ka thui.
\p 
\v 2 Vaiming a pakhehnah cawh va sei ka, a kaity cawh alui letah va tlaihly ka, sawhrang a tei cangnah ngianah a hnuipaw le ama a lopaw nono a behpaw sahlo cawh a hmui a chiahrupaw le a sah ngeteipaw hmawchia takhei a e he.
\p 
\v 3 Vaiming a pahningnah taco, a kaity cawh rili lekhei va tlaihly ka, tui cawh mehthi thi hrakhei a tua ka, rili chung letei a ungpaw hringnah a hnuipaw maikaw cawh a thi thlu he.
\p 
\v 4 Vaiming a pathungnah taco, a kaity cawh tuivaw le tuihnaw lekhei va tlaihly ka, tui cawh thisai tah a tua he.
\v 5 Mataico tui a mingkaipaw vaiming takhei,
\q1 “Nama cawh a ung leimeipaw le a ung thahpaw,
\q2 Mehpathai na cang.
\q1 Nama cawh na biacepanah sahlo lehei na ding,
\q2 zecawtamaw tatah dingná tah bia na ce.
\q1 
\v 6 Zecawtamaw tatah aaning taco na mehpathai sahlo le Khazing khuavang sahlo khah aa thisai laisah he ka,
\q2 Nama tah peh phu a cangpaw he thisai khah ding pawtah na peh myca he,”
\m a tahpaw khah ka thui.
\v 7 Taico dangnah siasang taitei chainah o tah,
\q1 “A cang, Abuipaw Khazing Zezong Tuatu,
\q2 na biacenah cawh a dihpaw le a dingpaw a cang,”
\m a tahpaw khah ka thui.
\p 
\v 8 Vaiming a papalinah taco, a kaity khah ning cung letah tlaihly ka, ning cawh me tah cawngsaw a kang khypaw hmingtuakhynah khah peh a cang.
\v 9 Aaning sahlo cawh a sah ngeteipaw palingnah takhei kangpa-uh he ka, ma hrehnah sahlo cung letei naw a hnuitu Khazing ming khah aa reipachia, canghrasala a ngepachih tah ama khah parungnawsah du hlui bei he.
\p 
\v 10 Vaiming a papangawnah takhei, a kaity cawh sawhrang abui dyching lekhei tlaihly ka, a painah raang cawh muinah tah a bakhu. Cawngsaw cawh aa taithui tunah cawtah aa lui khah ty he ka,
\v 11 taithuinah aa ingpaw le hmawchia aa ingpaw rawng takhei, vaicung Khazing khah aa pachia aa pahru. Canghrasala aa tuasapaw hming caw tei a ngepachih khah du hlui bei he.
\p 
\v 12 Vaiming a paruhnah takhei, a kaity cawh Zufreti tuivaw pui letah tlaihly ka, tui cawh kih ka, nichualang tei siangpahrang sahlo aa langpui ruapaw takhei a tua he.
\v 13 Mataico ca-uh ky a lopaw thlawpaw pialuipaw sangthung ka hmuh he. Aaning sahlo cawh paribui kaw le sawhrang kaw le khuavang pakheipaw kaw taikhei aa kapiapaw a cang he.
\v 14 Aaning sahlo cawh ningang chuipaw paching pakhanah a tuapaw khachia thlawpaw cang he ka, Khazing Zezong Tuatu ning rungnawpaw ning letah a dy he seh tah pawtah khazaw siangpahrang sahlo pahmo rua pawtah a sei he.
\p 
\v 15 “Ngetua, mehru hratah ka vong a! A hrah thlang katei, a chaichi raering teitah a chia thlangpaw cawngsaw cawh bonghnang a ting, ma pawsui co, ama cawh thlekalong tah le muaphy tah ung be,” a tah.
\p 
\v 16 Mataico siangpahrang sahlo khah Hebru rei tei Armagedon aa tahpaw hminghmaw lekhei thlawpaw pialuipaw sahlo takhei hmingkheh tah aa pahmo he.
\p 
\v 17 Taico, a hningcaipaw vaiming a pasarihnah takhei, a kaity cawh zizaw lekhei tlaihly ka, behnah ing chung letei Abui dyching taikhei o va ring ka, “A chang myca!” tatah a tah.
\v 18 Mataico lailaw va ky, o va ring, khalung a thih tah ka, aling a rupui tah a hrui. Alui lehei cawngsaw aa ungnah taitah ma tluh a rupaw aling cawh a hrui bang be.
\v 19 Alaipaw khuapui cawh chythung tah a chy ka, raang sahlo letei khuapui sahlo cawh a rawh cehceh he. Khazing tah Babilon khuapui cawh a thui thlang ka, a thingaenah misurhang zu tei a chihpaw ny khah ama cawh a dingsah.
\v 20 Tuiraw raang maikaw cawh ly thlu he ka, tlaang sahlo cawh hmuh khy cang khawh bei he.
\v 21 Avai taitah pong zakheh hrawnghrang a rihpaw aria alaipaw pui sahlo khah cawngsaw cung letah a tlah he. Taico aria tah hrehnah rawng taco Khazing khah aa reipachia, zecawtamaw tatah ma hrehnah cawh a saw tunah cawtah a cang.
\c 17
\s1 Sawhrang cung letei canu
\p 
\v 1 Vaiming pasarih hrong letei kaity sangsarih a hnuipaw pakheh khah a vong ka, ka hai letah, “A vong, tui hlupui cung letei a ty no, a ming a thangpaw hlohlangno hreh nápaw ka ca hmuh sá a.
\v 2 Alui bui sahlo cawh ama khatah a phei he ka, alui a pahrangpaw cawngsaw sahlo taco, aa suanah misur zu khah aa rui thlu,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 3 Mataico vaiming taco Thlawpaw khei raangcaa lang a pa seikhui. Ma leco Khazing reipachianah ming sahlo tei a pungpaluh a chih thlangpaw, lu lusarih le ki kihraw a hnuipaw sawhrang a saidungpaw cung letei a tythlangpaw canuno khah ka hmuh.
\v 4 Ma canuno cawh a saidungpaw le a saipaw chaichi khah a tua ka, sui le lungva a mai a rupaw le lungnaw khei a pasang. A kih letah a hohenah pasih padawh a chuipaw le a pialuipaw tei a chihpaw sui ny a tle.
\v 5 Ma biaparuh ming heh a pangcarih letah a khai.
\q1 “ Babilon khuapui rungnaw hlohlangno sahlo no
\q2 le alui letei pasih padawh a chuipaw sahlo no,”
\m tahpaw a cia.
\v 6 Ma canuno cawh Zisu ming a dawkhuipaw mehpathai sahlo thisai a ruipaw khah ka hmuh.
\p Ama cawh ka hmuh tihtah ka khuarawh a haa.
\v 7 Mataico vaiming tah, “Zecawtamaw na khuarawh a haa? Biathuh a cangpaw ma cawngsawno le a kepaw sawhrang a lu lusarih le ki kihraw a hnuipaw kong heh ka ca ching a.
\v 8 Na hmuhpaw sawhrang cawh khuahlai tah za hring ka, ato cawh hring khawh beh. Ama cawh a ping thai lypaw mehthi khua khobatlung taitah ka pia a ka, hlyde a cang a. Khazaw tua hlai taitei hringnah cabu letah ming cia a cang lypaw, alui a pahrangpaw sahlo taco ma sawhrang heh aa hmuh tihtah aa khuarawh a haa tae a, zecawtamaw tatah ama cawh khuahlai tah za hring ka, atoheh cawh hring khaw beh. A cang naná tah a va chuh kaw lepaw a cang.
\p 
\v 9 Ma lehei sing le vang a hy. Lu lusarih cawh ma canuno a tynah tlaang sangsarih tahnah a cang.
\v 10 Siangpahrang pasarih zong a cang hrah he. Siangpahrang papangawpaw sahlo cawh thi thah he ka, siangpahrang a paruhnah cawh ato leteipaw heh a cang, a tangpaw cawh va chuh balang be, canghrasala a va chua tihtah cai a cuitei longlong a ung a.
\v 11 Khuahlai tah za hring katei, atoheh a hring khawh lypaw sawhrang cawh siangpahrang a parehnah a cang. Siangpahrang pasarih letei a tae hrahpaw khah cang ka, a rawhrang palang a.
\p 
\v 12 Ki kihraw na hmuhpaw cawh painah raang a hnui balang lypaw siangpahrang pahraw khah cang he ka, canghrasala sawhrang khatah suimehlang pakheh chung uh hrui rua pawtah naw aa hnui a.
\v 13 Tingaipaw sangkheh hnui he ka, aa hmingtuakhynah le nawhnuinah cawh sawhrang khah aa peh a.
\v 14 Tuu teitei khah aa dy a, canghrasala Tuu teitei takhei a te he a, zecawtamaw tatah Ama cawh abui sahlo cung letah Abui, siangpahrang sahlo cung letah Siangpahrang a cangnah cawtah, taico Ama a hningzuitu sahlo, thingpaw le zingchuipaw tahpaw sahlo cawh Ama khatah a ung he a,” tatah a pa tah.
\p 
\v 15 Mataico vaiming taco, “Na hmuhpaw tui, hlohlangno a tynah kheh cawh mingphing sahlo, mingzawpui sahlo le raang sahlo le reikaw sahlo a cang he.
\v 16 Na hmuhpaw sawhrang le a ki kihraw takhei hlohlangno cawh a hua he ka, a hnuipaw vytei chu he ka, thlekalong tah aa chia a. A ngaisaw khah e he ka, me tah aa ro a.
\v 17 Zecawtamaw tatah Khazing a tingpaw a tling nápawtah ma tua dunah cawh aa lungthing chung letah Khazing tah a khung. Macawtaco Khazing bia a tling hlai chung cawh uhnah a hmingtuakhynah khah sawhrang peh cawh aa naw a tlah.
\v 18 Na hmuhpaw canuno cawh alui siangpahrang sahlo a uhpaw he khuapui rungnawpaw khah a cang,” tatah a pa tah.
\c 18
\s1 Babilon khuapui rorangnah
\p 
\v 1 Ma khy taico, vaiming ahringpaw vaicung taitah a za cungpaw khah hmuh neh ka, ama cawh nawhnuinah alai ngeteipaw khah hnui ka, alui cawh a rungnawná tah a khai thlu.
\v 2 A thaw duná tah y ka,
\q1 “Babilon khuapui rungnawpaw cawh rorang a cang myca! Rorang a cang myca!
\q2 Khachia sahlo ungnah le
\q1 thlawpaw pialuipaw cinglainah tah le
\q2 a pathai lypaw pavaw sahlo\f + \fr 18:2 \ft A pathai lypaw pavaw sahlo cawh, pahmu le langtaw le ra-aw sahlo, a cang he.\f* ungnah takhei a tua myca.
\q1 
\v 3 Zecawtamaw tatah raangting tah
\q2 a hohenah misur zu khah ding he ka, aa rui thlu.
\q1 Alui siangpahrang sahlo tah ama khaco canu capaw suanah tua he ka,
\q2 alui chohrawng sahlo cawh ohluikhaw tei a hohenah hnuichia khei aa rung thlu myca he,”
\m a tah.
\p 
\v 4 Mataico vaicung taitei o hringpaw ka thuipaw taco,
\q1 “Ka cawngsaw sahlo, ama no taikhei va piachua la,
\q2 mataico a suanah letah a hlo bei he ceh,
\q2 ruhanah rawrungpaw zong khah ing hra bei ceh.
\q1 
\v 5 Zecawtamaw tatah a suanah taco avai tong myca ka,
\q2 a chahlynah sahlo khah Khazing tah a thui thlang.
\q1 
\v 6 A ca tuatypaw he hrakhei ama cawh palei kaw my lo.
\q2 A tuapaw cawtah khei a lehning tah palei kaw my lo.
\q2 A ny lekhei a lehning tah a chongpaw zu khah tlaipah kaw my lo.
\q1 
\v 7 Rungnawnah le anawngnah zia khah ama teitah a pehpaw zékhei taithuinah le
\q2 lung reithuinah khah pei my lo.
\q1 A lungchung tah a palai a patui ka,
\q2 ‘Siangpahrang no hratah a typaw ka cang,
\q2 lahme cang bei neh, ngechianah a tong by bei neh,’ a tah.
\q1 
\v 8 Macawtaco ningkheh chung tah
\q2 thihnah le mangchiasahnah le cakaangná tah dangtah a cang a.
\q1 Me tah a kang thlu a, zecawtamaw tatah ama bia a pacepaw cawh
\q2 a thawtlungpaw Abuipaw Khazing khah a cang.
\p 
\v 9 Ama khatah canu capaw suanah tua he katei, a nawngse tah a ung hruipaw alui siangpahrang sahlo takhei ama a kangpaw mekhu khah aa hmuh tihtah ngechia tah aa cawkhui a.
\v 10 Taithuinah a ingpaw khah aa cinah cawtah langpa tah a daw he ka,
\q1 ‘Na cing a ping! Vy khuapui rungnaw, na cing a ping!
\q2 Vy Babilon hmingtuakhynah khuapui!
\q1 Suimehlang pakheh chung letah dangtahnah tah a ca tlungso hi!’
\m aa tah.
\p 
\v 11 Alui chohrawng sahlo taco ama cawh cawkhui he ka, mangchia aa sah khui a, zecawtamaw tatah aa cho a co ruapaw ung khaw bei he.
\v 12 Aa cho cawh sui, ngung, lungva a mai a rupaw le lungnaw sahlo; pai anaipaw, a saidungpaw, pupai le asaipaw pai, ringthopaw thing a phingphing le alai nua, a mai a rupaw thing, daa, thaw le lungrang tei tuapaw hming a phingphing,
\v 13 thingesing, masala, ringthopaw, a ringthopaw a tahpaw mura le frankinsen, misur zu le oliv sathy le vedi le changvuh, co le tuu, rang le ranglai, sae le ahringpaw cawngsaw a cang he.
\p 
\v 14 Aaning sahlo taco, ‘Na dupaw hmingchaw vytei cawh a ly thlu myca he. Na rungnah vytei le na rungnawnah huhang vytei zong a ly thlu myca he. Ma hming sahlo heh zening tahmai va chuh kaw khaw bei he,’ aa tah a.
\v 15 Ma hming a zuatu chohrawng sahlo, ama thong tei a hnuirungpaw sahlo takhei a taithuinah khah ci he ka, langhlaw taitah cai he ka, cah he ka, mangchia aa sah a,
\v 16 taico,
\q1 ‘Na cing a ping! Na cing a ping! Vy khuapui rungnaw,
\q2 pai anaipaw, a saidungpaw le asaipaw pai khei a pasang ceh ka,
\q2 a tlypaw sui le a mai a rupaw lungva le lungnaw tei a pasang teipaw cawh!
\q1 
\v 17 Ma tluh hnuirungnah khah suimehlang pakheh chung letah a lyde thlang!’
\m tatah a cah he.
\p Tuilawng hotu le tuilawng tei khua a tlawng teipaw sahlo, tuilawng khaetu sahlo, rili taitei po cawngnah hlo a hmuhpaw vytei cawh langhlaw pui tah aa ung.
\v 18 Aa ronahpaw mekhu khah aa hmuh tihtah, ‘Ma khuapui rungnawpaw hapaw khuapui heh a ung bang maw?’ aa tah a.
\v 19 Aa ngechianah palang pawtah luipadih khah aa lu letah a bia he ka, caw hmo le mangchiasah hmotah y he ka,
\q1 ‘Na cing a ping! Na cing a ping! Vy khuapui rungnaw,
\q2 rili letah tuilawng a hnuipaw maikaw cawh
\q2 na hnuirungná khei aa rung thlu he!
\q1 Suimehlang pakheh chung lekhei khuapui cawh rorang a cang thah!
\q1 
\v 20 Vy vaicung letah a ungpaw le
\q2 mehpathai sahlo le apostol sahlo le Khazing khuavang sahlo, a lawng tua o!
\q1 Naa cung letei a tuasenah vytei rawng takhei ama cawh Khazing tah bia a cepah myca hi!’
\m aa tah a,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 21 Mataico, a thawtlungpaw vaiming takhei saangrianah lungtung alaipaw pui hapaw alung khah cui ka, rili lang vathlang ka,
\q1 “Ma hrahei Babilon khuapui rungnaw cawh
\q2 ringthimi tah rorang cang ka,
\q2 hmuh kaw cang khaw be.
\q1 
\v 22 Tingtang a tung thaipaw sahlo le hlaw a sahpaw sahlo o le phipahli a tung thaipaw sahlo le hmoka a tung thaipaw sahlo tei aa tungpaw py cawh
\q2 na chung letah thui cang khaw be.
\q1 Rai a hrepaw sahlo
\q2 na chung letah hmuh cang khaw bei he.
\q1 Sangrianah py cawh
\q2 na chung letah thui cang khawh by be.
\q1 
\v 23 Me-ing a khainah cawh na chung letah khai khaw be.
\q1 Nupui a chuipaw satle le pasae a hnuipaw laisaw o cawh
\q2 na chung letah thui cang khaw be.
\q1 Na chohrawng sahlo cawh khazaw mehlai sahlo a cang he.
\q2 Na ca-ia khei mingphing vytei cawh lang lypaw lang hrui a cang thlu myca he.
\q1 
\v 24 Khazing khuavang sahlo le mehpathai sahlo le
\q2 aluicung letei thawpaw sahlo vytei thisai khah nama letah hmuh a cang he,”
\m a tah.
\c 19
\s1 Hallelujah!
\p 
\v 1 Ma khy taico vaicung letah cawngsaw rungpui ysangpaw o hapaw pyraw cawh thui neh ka,
\q1 “Hallelujah!
\q1 Pachahnah le rungnawnah le hmingtuakhynah cawh kaa Khazing a tei a cang,
\q2 
\v 2 zecawtamaw tatah a biacenah cawh a dingpaw le ahmangpaw a cang.
\q1 A pheilalai nápaw tah alui a papia a paluipaw mingthang hlohlangno khah
\q2 thaily a cangsah myca.
\q1 A sae sahlo aa thisai cawh ama tah phu a hlang myca,”
\m tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 3 Taico,
\q1 “Hallelujah!
\q1 Ama a kangpaw mekhu cawh chaizaw tah chaizaw tai a khu paria thlang,”
\m tatah aa y vy hui.
\p 
\v 4 Macang paki papali le hminghring sangpali cawh aa khuh panai he ka, abui dyching letah a tythlangpaw Khazing khah aa beh. Taico,
\q1 “Amen, Hallelujah!”
\m tatah a y he.
\p 
\v 5 Mataico abui dyching taitah o va ring ka,
\q1 “Naaning Khazing a sae a cangpaw,
\q2 Ama a cizawpaw vytei,
\q1 mehchia le, mehlai,
\q2 kaa Khazing cawh reithai my lo!”
\m aa tah.
\p 
\v 6 Mataico, cawngsaw rungpui py a lopaw, tuiraso py le khalung a thihpaw py a lopaw thui neh ka,
\q1 “Hallelujah!
\q2 Kaa Buipaw Khazing Zezong Tuatu tah a uh myca.
\q1 
\v 7 A nawng he peh seh la, a lawng he peh,
\q2 taico Ama cawh rungnawnah pei he peh!
\q1 Zecawtamaw tatah Tuu teitei nupui chui cai cawh phah myca ka,
\q2 nupui chui ruapaw laisawno zong a mai myca.
\q1 
\v 8 Pai anaipaw, akhaipaw le a pathaipaw cawh
\q2 a pasangnah rua pawtah peh a cang myca,”
\m tatah aa y. Pai anaipaw cawh mehpathai sahlo dingnah tuanah cai pawtah hmangpaw a cang.
\p 
\v 9 Mataico vaiming takhei, “Cia tua, Tuu teitei nupuichuinah kawngchua letah hruipaw sahlo cawh bonghnang aa ting a,” a pa tah. Taico, “Ma sahlo heh Khazing biahmuisui cawh a cang he,” a tah vy.
\p 
\v 10 Ma tih taco a phehrang letah ka khuh panai neh ka, beh ka pachia. Canghrasala, “Pa beh kheh! Kama cawh nama le Zisu a bia a tle thlangpaw na uny sahlo hratah raihretu ka cang. Khazing long khah beh! Zecawtamaw tatah phyhlangpaw bia vytei a lemari cawh Zisu hnikhuipaw bia taitah a cang,” tatah a pa tah.
\s1 Rang rang a kepaw
\p 
\v 11 Mataico, vaicung a hongpaw hmuh neh ka, ma leco ka hme letah a ungpaw cawh rang araangpaw cang ka, a ketupaw cawh Zingchuipaw le Biahmuisui tatah aa y. Dingná tah biapace ka, rae a tuh.
\v 12 A meh cawh mesy hratah cang ka, a lu letah builukhu hlupui a khu. A pung cung letah ming a cia ka, ma cawh ama tah ly co ahotahmai a silang hnih bei he.
\v 13 Thisai letah nongpaw angki pasuapaw a hrei ka, a ming cawh Khazing Bia a cang.
\v 14 Vaicung raekeh sahlo takhei aa pazui lai ke ka, rang raang ke he ka, pai anaipaw, araangpaw le a pathaipaw a buh he.
\v 15 A kaw taikhei zyzi a te ngeteipaw ka pia ka, raangting a chawhly thlu he a. Aaning sahlo cawh thaw cungcahrei tah a uh he a. Khazing Zezong Tuatu a thingaenah misur sonah kho leco a phe tah a ci he.
\v 16 A angki pasuapaw le a bawng letah, “Siangpahrang sahlo cung letah Siangpahrang le abui sahlo cung letah Abui,” tahpaw ming heh a cia.
\p 
\v 17 Taico ning letah vaiming a daw thlangpaw khah ka hmuh, ama taco avai letei a zythi laipaw pavaw sahlo vytei khah, “A vong la, Khazing tei a tuapaw lawhdangnah rungnawpaw leco a va pahmo tua o,
\v 18 siangpahrang sahlo, raekeh bui sahlo, a thawtlungpaw cawngsaw sahlo, rang sahlo le a kepaw sahlo, cawngsaw vytei, sae le mehlua, mehlai mehchia aa saw sahlo e ná he ceh seh,” tatah a thangpui tah a tah he.
\p 
\v 19 Mataico, sawhrang le alui siangpahrang sahlo le aa raekeh sahlo cawh rang a kepaw le a raekeh sahlo rae thohno rua pawtah hmingkheh tah a pahmopaw he khah ka hmuh.
\v 20 Canghrasala, sawhrang cawh tle cang ka, ama khaco ama caipaw tei ningang chuipaw paching pakhanah a tua teipaw khuavang pakheipaw khah tle a cang hrah. Ma paching pakhanah sahlo taco, sawhrang a tei cangnah ngianah hnui katei, a nono a behpaw sahlo khah a dungkhei he. Aaning pahning cawh kaa-me tuili lang ahringpaw tah thlah a cang he.
\v 21 A raekeh sahlo cawh rang a kepaw a kaw taitei a kapiapaw zyzi khei thaw cang he ka, pavaw vytei tah aa saw cawh rivaw teitah aa e he.
\c 20
\s1 Kung thongkheh
\p 
\v 1 Taico vaicung taitah a za cung chuhpaw vaiming, a ping thai lypaw mehthi khua khobatlung cabi a kai katei, bahrairui alaipaw pui a kih letah a tle thlangpaw khah ka hmuh.
\v 2 Ama taco paribui cawh tle ka, ma cawh khachia, khuahlai paribui Setan khah cang ka, kung thongkheh chung a hrai thlang.
\v 3 Ama cawh a ping thai lypaw mehthi khua khobatlung lang khah thlah ka, kung thongkheh a chang hlai vytei raang sahlo a dungkhei khawh ly nápaw he tah khobatlung khah hrai ka, a cung letah cakhai a khai. Ma khy taico cai cuitei cawtah ama cawh thlaw a cang tae a.
\p 
\v 4 Taico, biacenah nawhnuinah peh a cangpaw sahlo abui dyching sahlo letah a ty thlangpaw he khah ka hmuh. Zisu a dawkhui rawng he tah le Khazing bia aa rei rawng tei aa lu aa taipaw thlawpaw sahlo zong khah ka hmuh he. Aaning sahlo cawh sawhrang a cang ly leh a nono khah beh be ca he ka, aa pangcarih letah a cang ly leh aa kih letah a tei cangnah ngianah zong hnui bei he. Aaning sahlo cawh hring kaw he ka, Khri khatah kung thongkheh raang aa uh a.
\v 5 Ma heh thokawnah hmasawtawpaw cawh a cang. A tangpaw a thipaw sahlo cawh kung thongkheh cai a chang hlai taco hring kaw bei he.
\v 6 Thokawnah hmasawtawpaw letei a taepaw sahlo cawh a pathaipaw le bonghnang a tingpaw a cang he. Uihning thihnah tah aa cung letah hmingtuakhynah hnui be, Khazing le Khri tlangbui cang hri he ka, Ama khatah kung thongkheh aa uh a.
\s1 Setan a sung
\p 
\v 7 Kung thongkheh cawh a chang tihtah Setan cawh hrai a cangnahpaw taikhei thlaw cang ka,
\v 8 Gog le Magok aa tahpaw alui pungpaluh taitei raangting khah dungkhei pawtah le raetuh rua pawtah pahmo pawtah aa sei a. Aa hlu zia cawh rili ngaekang letei sadi zeh a cang he a.
\v 9 Aluicung khah cahrong tah sei he ka, Khazing a cawngsaw sahlo aa ungnahpaw khua, Khazing a dopaw khuapui khah aa cadung. Canghrasala avai taitah me za tlah ka, aaning sahlo cawh a kangseh thlu he.
\v 10 Taico Setan, aaning sahlo a dungkheipaw he cawh kaa-me tuiping lang khah thlah a cang, ma cawh sawhrang le khuavang pakheipaw aa thlahnah pawhe khah a cang. Aaning sahlo cawh ching kha, zai kha chaizaw tah chaizaw tai aa taithui paria thlang a.
\s1 Mehthi biacenah
\p 
\v 11 Mataico a rungnaw ngeteipaw buidyching araangpaw le a cung letei a typaw khah ka hmuh. Alui le avai cawh a hmekaw taitah a hneihly he ka, aa cawtah hminghmaw ung khawh be.
\v 12 Taico mehthi vytei, mehlai mehchia, abui dyching hme letah a daw thlangpaw he hmuh neh ka, taico cabu sahlo cawh a pakai thlangpaw khah ka hmuh. Taico ahringpaw cabu khah pakai he ka, ma cawh hringnah cabu a cang. Mehthi sahlo cawh cabu sahlo letei khungpaw aa tuasanah naning khei biacepah a cang he.
\v 13 Rili taco a chung letei a thipaw sahlo khah papia he ka, thihnah le Mehthi khua takhei a chung letei a thipaw sahlo khah papia he ka, mingting cawh aa tuasanah naning khei biacepah a cang he.
\v 14 Mataico, thihnah le Mehthi khua cawh me tuiping lang thlah a cang he. Me tuiping cawh thihnah uihningnah a cang.
\v 15 Hringnah cabu letei a ming hmuh lypaw maikaw cawh me tuiping lang thlah a cang he.
\c 21
\s1 Jerusalem thapaw
\p 
\v 1 Mataico, alui thapaw le avai thapaw hmuh neh ka, alui hmasawtawpaw le avai hmasawtawpaw cawh ly thah he ka, rili zong khah ung khawh be.
\v 2 A pathaipaw khuapui, Jerusalem thapaw cawh a pasae a tong rua pawtei a chaichi a nge ngetei pawtei a pasangpaw laisawno hratah a pachia ka, Khazing taitah vaicung taitei a za cungpaw khah ka hmuh.
\v 3 Taico buidyching taitah o a thangpaw pui thui neh ka, “Atoheh cawh Khazing ungnah ing khah cawngsaw khatah ung myca ka, Ama cawh aaning khatah a ung myca a. Aaning sahlo cawh a cawngsaw cang he ka, Khazing Ama hrahring cawh aaning khatah ung ka, aa Khazing a cang a.
\v 4 Ama taco, aa meh letei mehthli khah a hrupah thlu he a. Thihnah le ngechianah le cawnah le asawnah ung khaw be, zecawtamaw tatah hming paringpaw sahlo cawh a ly myca he,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 5 Ma buidyching letei a tythlangpaw taco, “Zezong maikaw a thapaw tah ka tua leimei he,” tatah a tah. Mataico, “Ma heh cia, zecawtamaw tatah ma bia heh zingchuipaw le ahmangpaw a cang,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 6 Ama taco ka hai letah, “Zezongpui paling a cang myca. Kama cawh Alfa le Omeka, Ahrangthonah le Achangnah ka cang. A tui a hraepaw cawh hringnah a peipaw tuihnaw taitei tui khah a mai lytah ding pawtah ka pae a.
\v 7 Tetu a cangpaw sahlo tah ma vytei heh cy he ka, kama cawh aa Khazing cang neh ka, aaning cawh ka sawcapaw a cang he a.
\v 8 Canghrasala mehraechia, zingnah a hnui lypaw, pasihpadawh chuipaw, lenongpaw, canu capaw suanah a tuapaw, ca-ia a thaipaw, nono a behpaw le hingbia a reipaw vytei aa hminghmaw cawh kaa-me tuili cichui ngeteipaw a cang tae a. Ma heh thihnah uihningnah cawh a cang,” tatah a pa tah.
\p 
\v 9 Vaiming pasarih hrong letei ruhanah rawrungpaw hningcaipaw sangsarih tei a chihpaw kaity sangsarih a hnuipaw pakheh cawh a vong ka, ka hai letah, “A vong tua, pasae hnui a pachiapaw laisawno, Tuu teitei a nupuino ruapaw cawh ka ca hmuhsah a,” tatah a pa tah.
\v 10 Taico, vaiming taco Thlawpaw khei tlaang a sangpaw pui le alaipaw pui lang khah a pa seikhui. A pathaipaw khuapui, Jerusalem, Khazing taitei vaicung taitah a za cungpaw khah a pa hmuhsah.
\v 11 Ma khuapui cawh Khazing rungnawná tah khai ka, lungva a mai sung ngeteipaw jaspar lungva hratah khai ngetei ka, kristal alung hratah a pasing ngetei.
\v 12 Ruahy alaipaw pui, a sang ngeteipaw hnui ka, hawkaw kaw hrawhluihning a ung. Ma hawkaw kaw hrawhluihning leco vaiming hluihning a ung he. Hawkaw sahlo cung leco Israel phinghraw hluihning ming khah a cia.
\v 13 Ma hawkaw sahlo cawh nichualang letah kawthung, nitlah lang letah kawthung, thuilang letah kawthung, tlanglang letah kawthung a cang he.
\v 14 Khuapui ruahy cawh a pahnianah alung sanghrawhluihning cung letah sah cang ka, sangkheh cy cung leco Tuu teitei apostol pahrawhluihning ming kheh cy a khai he.
\p 
\v 15 Kama bia a pa chingpaw vaiming cawh khuapui le a hawkaw sahlo le a ruahy neh nápawtah khei sui basung a tle.
\v 16 Khuapui cawh a ki kipali a cangpaw, a tung le vang a khingpaw a cang. Nehnah basung khei vaiming taco khuapui cawh neh ka, a tung le a vang le a sang cawh khang 1,500 cy aa cang he.
\v 17 Ruahy khah cawngsaw hmangpaw neh ná khei, vaiming tah neh ka, pei 200 hrawng a sang.
\v 18 Ruahy cawh jaspar lungva tah rua cang ka, khuapui cawh thlalang tluá tei a pasingpaw sui pathai tah tuapaw a cang.
\v 19 Khuapui ruahy a pahnianah alung sahlo cawh alung maisung a phingphing khei pasang a cang he. A pahnianah hmetawpaw cawh ahringpaw lungva jaspar, a sanghningnah cawh adungpaw lungva safaiar, a sangthungnah cawh lungva chaldoni, a sangpalinah cawh ahringpaw lungva emerald,
\v 20 a sangpangawnah cawh sardonik lungva, a sangruhnah cawh asaipaw lungva karnelian, a sangsarihnah cawh ahringpaw lungva krisolai, a sangrehnah cawh ahringpaw lungva beril, a sangkuanah cawh amaipaw lungva topaz, a sanghrawnah cawh ahringpaw lungva krisoprai, a hluikhehnah cawh asaipaw lungva jasin, a hluihningnah cawh a saidungpaw lungva ametis a cang he.
\v 21 Hawkaw hluihning cawh lungnaw hluihning a cang he, kawkheh cacy cawh lungnaw sangkheh cy tah tuapaw a cang he. Khuapui letei langlaipui cawh thlalang tluá tei a pasingpaw sui pathaipaw tah tuapaw a cang.
\p 
\v 22 Khuapui chung letaco behnah ing hmuh bei neh, zecawtamaw tatah Abuipaw Khazing Zezong Tuatu le Tuu teitei cawh a behnah ing a cang he.
\v 23 Khuapui taco, a cung letah a khai rua pawtah ning khah hia be ca ka, thlawpaw zawng hia hrah beh, zecawtamaw tatah, Khazing rungnawnah takhei khaisah ka, Tuu teitei cawh a me-ing a cang.
\v 24 Aluicung cawngsaw vytei tah a khainah lekhei a khia he ka, alui siangpahrang sahlo taco aa laisuinah khah a chunglang a naekhui he a.
\v 25 Ma leco, hawkaw aa kha tahpaw ung khawh a be, zecawtamaw tatah ma leco zai ung khawh beh.
\v 26 Taico, mingphing sahlo rungnawnah le palawngpalinah cawh a chunglang a naekhui a cang tae a.
\v 27 A pathai lypaw zehmai a chunglang a nae be, ningzaw chuipaw a cang ly leh dungkhei a hmangpaw ahohmai a nae hrá bei he. Canghrasala Tuu teitei hringnah cabu chung letei ming ciapaw sahlo suipaw a nae he a.
\c 22
\s1 Hringnah tuivaw
\p 
\v 1 Taico, vaiming taco thlalang tluá tei pasing katei hringnah a peipaw tui a laipaw tuivaw a pa hmusah. Ma tuivaw cawh Khazing le Tuu teitei buidyching taikhei khuapui langlaipui a lecingcing khei a za laipaw a cang.
\v 2 Tuivaw a kang le kang co hringnah thingkung ung he ka, thlah kheh phingkheh leimei tah thlah hrawhluihning chung a thui a thui he. Taico thingkung aa hnaw sahlo cawh mingphing sahlo dangnah cawtah aa hmang he.
\v 3 Ma leco chiasah ung khaw be. Khuapui leco Khazing abui dyching le Tuu teitei buidyching ung ka, taico a sae sahlo takhei Ama khah aa be a.
\v 4 Aaning sahlo taco a hme hmuh a he ka, a ming cawh aa pangcarih letah aa cia he a.
\v 5 Ma leco zai ung khaw be. Aaning sahlo taco me-ing khainah tlawng maw, ning khainah tlawng maw hia khaw bei he, zecawtamaw tatah Abuipaw Khazing tah khainah a pae he. Taico aaning sahlo taco chaizaw tah chaizaw tai aa uh a.
\p 
\v 6 Taico vaiming taco ka hai letah, “Ma bia heh zingchuipaw le ahmangpaw a cang. Abuipaw, Khazing khuavang thlawpaw sahlo aa Khazing taco, ry lytah a tlung palangpaw hming sahlo khah a sae sahlo hmuhsah rua pawtah a vaiming khah a za tawpaw a cang,” tatah a pa tah.
\s1 Zisu a vong pating a
\p 
\v 7 “Ngetua, ka vong pating a! Ma cabu letei phyhlangpaw bia sahlo a zuipaw cawh bonghnang a ting a,” tatah Zisu tah a tah.
\p 
\v 8 Ma hming sahlo heh hmuh katei a thuipaw cawh kama Johan heh ka cang. Taico ma sahlo heh hmuh neh katei, ka thui tihtah a pa hmuhsah tupaw vaiming cawh beh a pawtah a phehrang leco ka khuh ka panai.
\v 9 Canghrasala ama taco ka hai letah, “Pa beh kheh! Kama cawh nama le na uny Khazing khuavang sahlo le ma cabu leteipaw bia a zuipaw sahlo vytei hratah sae ka cang. Khazing khah beh hri!” tatah a pa tah.
\p 
\v 10 Mataico, ama taco, “Ma cabu letei phyhlangpaw bia sahlo heh nawh kheh, zecawtamaw tatah a cai a ne myca.
\v 11 Ahmang lypaw a tuapaw cawh ahmang lypaw hratah ung thlang seh la, mehpialui cawh mehpialui tah ung thlang seh, a dingpaw a tuapaw cawh a dingpaw khah tua paria thlang seh la, a pathaipaw cawh pathai paria thlang ky seh,” tatah a pa tah.
\p 
\v 12 “Ngetua, ka vong pating a! Ka longmai cawh a va tle neh ka, ming maikaw khah aa tuapaw naning tei hratah ka pae he a.
\v 13 Kama cawh Alfa le Omeka, Ahmasaw caipaw le Ahning caipaw, Ahrangthonah le A changnah ka cang,” tatah Zisu tah a tah.
\p 
\v 14 Aa pai a suh pathaipaw sahlo cawh bonghnang aa ting a, ma pawsui co hringnah thingkung taikhei e khy he ka, hawkaw lang khei khuapui chunglang cawh a nae khy he a.
\v 15 Khuapui alailang teipaw sahlo cawh ui sahlo, ca-ia a thaipaw sahlo, a pheilapaw sahlo, lenongpaw sahlo, nono a behpaw sahlo le hingbia a dupaw le a tuapaw sahlo a cang he.
\p 
\v 16 “Kama Zisu tah naaning khrisawbu sahlo khatah ma bia thuisah ruapaw tahei ka vaiming khah ka va taw. Kama cawh David Thahrang le a Teisaw le Duivaw esi khaipaw ka cang,” a tah.
\p 
\v 17 Thlawpaw le pasae hnui a zapaw laisawno taco, “A vong!” aa tah. Taico a thuipaw taco, “A vong!” tah hrah seh. A tui a hraepaw maikaw cawh a vong he seh. A dupaw vytei taco a mai ly tei pehpaw hringnah tui heh a lah he seh.
\p 
\v 18 Ma cabu letei phyhlangpaw bia a thuipaw maikaw khah ka ca thuisah he. Ahotahmai tah ma sahlo heh a chahchi caco, ama cawh Khazing tah ma cabu letei palang ciapaw ruhanah rawrungpaw khah a chahchi a.
\v 19 Taico ahotahmai tah ma cabu letei phyhlangpaw bia khah a lahly caco, ama cawh Khazing tah ma cabu letei palang ciapaw hringnah thingkung letei a ting vypaw le a pathaipaw khuapui letei a ting vypaw khah a lah pah hly hra a.
\p 
\v 20 Ma hming sahlo a hnikhuitu Zisu taco, “A cang, ka vong pating a,” a tah.
\p Amen. Abuipaw Zisu a vong myca!
\p 
\v 21 Abuipaw Zisu a ningdonah cawh Khazing a cawngsaw vytei khatah ung ky seh. Amen.
